Umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus (COVID-19) wiyongereye cyane muri EU/European Economic Area no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus disease (COVID-19) ugaragaza ko ibihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza bifite imiterere imwe, ibyo bikaba byemeza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera cyane mu bihugu byose, mu bihe bitandukanye bitewe n'igihugu.
Bitewe n'ibyabaye mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi cyane bigomba kongera imyiteguro ku kwiyongera gukomeye kw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazakenera kwitabwaho, cyane cyane ku barwayi bakomeye.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, itsinda ry'abantu barwaye pneumonia badafite ibimenyetso bizwi by'indwara, batangajwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, Ubushinwa cyatangaje ko coronavirus nshya, ubu yitwa SARS-CoV-2, ari yo ndwara yanduza.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yiswe indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibihamya ni uko 80% by'abantu bafite COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga indwara z'ubuhumekero ziterwa na Pneumonia cyangwa ntayo, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu barwayi 14%, COVID-19 ikomeza kuba indwara ikomeye cyane ikeneye kuvurwa mu bitaro mu gihe abandi 6% bagaragaza uburwayi bukomeye bukeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, tugenzuye uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwagiye bwiyongera muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza (UK) tugereranya n'intara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri iki gihe mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020 ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani.
Imibare ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yakomeje kwaguka mu by'ubutaka kandi ubu ibikorwa by'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi byitaruye icyo gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Icyiciro cyo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020 cya Eurosurveillance, Spiteri et al. cyatangaje ko habayeho ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwemejwe bwa mbere mu Burayi nk'uko byasobanuwe na WHO.
Mu karere ka EU/EEA, ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020, u Bufaransa bwagaragaje ko bwa mbere hari abantu batatu bemejwe ko banduye, bagaruka mu gihugu cyabo baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ibihugu byose 30 bya EU/EEA na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika (UK) byamaze kugaragaza ko byanduye COVID-19, mu gihe mu Butaliyani honyine hari hamaze kuboneka abanduye 17,750 n'abamaze gupfa 1,441 hamwe n'abamaze gupfa 39,768 n'abamaze gupfa 1,727 hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'iyo tariki.
Kugira umubare w'ibanze w'abanduye COVID-19 n'ubwiyongere bw'ibanze
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC), cyerekana imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 ya buri gihugu ku isi, igaruka ku isaha ya 8:00 za mu gitondo buri munsi, gusa ikorwa n'ibitangazamakuru byemewe nka Minisiteri y'Ubuzima y'ibihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'iz'akarere na OMS.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 igenda mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK no kuyigereranya n'iyo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uhagarariye ikwirakwira ry'ibyaha bya COVID-19 bikorera, dukurikije ibi, twabaze umubare w'ibyumweru 14 by'ibyago bya COVID-19 mu gihe cy'ukwezi kwa mbere kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, dufatiye ku buryo kamere bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Twerekanye kandi imibare y'ibanze y'abanduye muri buri gihugu kugeza saa munani za mu gitondo z'itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imyiteguro y'iminsi 14 y'ubwiyongere bw'ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, muri rusange ikurikirana intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Mu karere ka EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza hose, ubwandu rusange bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare kandi bwiyongera cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'izamuka ry'umubare w'abanduye batangajwe mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA na UK byerekanye ko hari ibintu byiyongera ku mubare w'abanduye COVID-19 (Ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'ibanze y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cyo ku ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibi byerekana by'umwihariko ko kugeza saa munani za mu gitondo z'itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibindi bihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byari bimaze gutangaza imibare y'abanduye yose hamwe, ingana n'iy'abari mu Butaliyani mu byumweru 3 gusa bishize cyangwa mu gihe gito.
Ibisubizo byacu byerekana ko imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 yiyongera cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Imiterere igaragara mu mubare w'abanduye COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo kirimo kwiyongera ku muvuduko ugereranyije mu bihugu byose.
Ibi ni nubwo ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, itandukaniro mu bisubizo by'ubuzima rusange by'igihugu, ibisobanuro by'ibibazo bishobora gutandukana mu bihugu, ndetse n'amabwiriza atandukanye yo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa by'ingenzi kugira ngo bamenyekane ko barwaye COVID-19, harimo no kubafata no kubagenzura.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga mu bice by'u Butaliyani byatewe n'icyorezo bavuze ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi cyane byamaze kugera ku bushobozi bwabyo.
Imibare y'ibitaro na/cyangwa kwinjizwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 muri iki gihe iraboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ku bantu 6% na 1% gusa (imibare ntiyerekanwe).
