Kubera ko kugeza ubu, hari umubare munini w'abanduye mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane bikorera abaturage babigenewe mu karere, amakuru ajyanye n'abanduye n'ibitanda by'abarwayi bababaye cyane bigomba gutangwa ku rwego rwa nomenclature y'ibice by'akarere by'ibarurishamibare 2 (NUTS-2).
Ubumenyi bwatanzwe n'u Butaliyani n'imiterere iriho mu bindi bihugu, bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye bigomba kwitegura guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ubwandu bw'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage no kwihanganira umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwita ku buzima, cyane cyane mu buvuzi bukabije nk'uko biri mu bice by'u Butaliyani byugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Nkuko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ry'ibyago bya ECDC riherutse, hamwe n'ihinduka ry'uburyo bwo kugabanya guhera ku kugabanya, uburyo bwihuse, bwihuse kandi bunini burakenewe mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2, kuko niba bitabaye mu gihe, ibyemezo byihuse byitezwe ku mubare w'abanduye bishobora kutaha igihe gihagije abatera n'ibitaro byo gusobanukirwa, kwemera no guhuza ibisubizo byabo.
