Icyorezo cya Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) cyatewe na SARS (Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome) Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 no kwanduza abantu barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bituma abantu bahura n'akaga.
Kimwe na virusi ya SARS-CoV, yatumye abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi bagerwaho na SARS mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yanduye ikoresheje udukoko kandi ikagira ibimenyetso nk'ibyo.
Nubwo COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'urupfu biri hasi ugereranyije na SARS, irandura cyane kandi ikagira ingaruka ku bantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato n'abagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare w'ibitabo by'imfashanyigisho ku ndwara zigenda zigaragara, iyi nyandiko igerageza gutanga isesengura rihoraho kandi ryimbitse ku ngingo y'ubushakashatsi igenda itera imbere.
Tuzashyiraho ibintu by'ibanze ku byerekeye indwara z'ibyorezo, impamvu, virusi, gusuzuma, kuvura, kubara no kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo hakiri ibibazo byinshi bigomba gusubizwa, twizeye ko iri suzuma rizadufasha gusobanukirwa iyi ndwara yica kandi tukayirandura.
Kubera icyorezo cy'indwara y'agakoko gashya, umunsi mukuru wa Spring Festival wabaye ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye ikintu kitazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu ngo zabo mu gihe cyose cy'ikiruhuko ndetse n'ibyumweru byinshi bikurikiyeho.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na Coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze cyane (SARS) mu 2003; bityo, ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryayise SARS-CoV-2 n'indwara ifitanye isano yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Icyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gikwirakwira mu gihugu hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, hamaze kuboneka abarwayi barenga 80,000 ba COVID-19 banduye iyi virusi, abarenga 40,000 barekuwe mu bitaro, abarenga 3,000 barapfa.
OMS yaburiye ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi wa rubanda wa mbere kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri nyuma y'aho hatangiriye raporo ya mbere yo ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, inyandiko zirenga 200 ku COVID-19 zagiye zisohoka, harimo Virology, Epidemiology, Forensics, Diagnostics, and Treatment, zigaragaza ko virusi yafashwe mu buryo butandukanye n'abarwayi benshi.
Iyi raporo igerageza kwerekana muri make iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi ku ngingo nshya kandi zigenda zihindagurika.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 n'indi ndwara iterwa na SARS na CoV, Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS, icyorezo mu 2012).
Tuzaganira ku byo twize kugeza ubu ku birebana no kwirinda no kwirinda indwara, ndetse n'ibindi bibazo bimwe na bimwe by'ingenzi.
CoVs zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe zitezwe kuba indwara zidakomeye ku bantu, zitera nibura 15% by'ibicurane 4.
Icyakora, muri iki kinyejana twahuye inshuro ebyiri na CoVs z'abantu ziteza indwara zikomeye, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye haduka icyorezo mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi bidatinze cyakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu byinshi, kigahitana abantu benshi.
Bityo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka yanditswe y'abantu.
Nkuko bigaragara mu ishusho ya 1.1, ibicurane bya Pneumonia, bitamenyekanye inkomoko yabyo, byatangajwe bwa mbere na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Ubushinwa ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 ivuye i Wuhan.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, hashyizwe ahagaragara urutonde rwa CoV.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umuntu wa mbere wanduye yavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu bituranye.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima batangajwe ko banduye, byerekana ko ubwandu bw'abantu bushobora gutandukana.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan wafunzwe hamwe n'ingendo zose rusange.
Mu bushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe kuri iki cyorezo ku ya 24 Mutarama, byatangajwe ko mu barwayi 41 bafite ubwandu bwemejwe, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye mu buryo butaziguye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, ryitwa ko ari ryo ryatangiye kwandura indwara iturutse ku nkoko zitazwi.
