Urugero, ibi bigo bigomba (1) kwitonda cyane mu gihe bitanga amatangazo y'abaturage kuko ijambo ryose rifite agaciro ku baturage kandi rishobora guhindura imyumvire n'imyanzuro yabo; (2) kurushaho kumva no kwitabira amakuru adasanzwe aturuka mu mavuriro aho gutegereza amakuru yemewe n'abaganga cyangwa abayobozi; (3) kurushaho gukumira icyorezo gishobora kubaho mu gihe cy'intangiriro aho kugerageza guhumuriza abaturage; no (4) gutangiza imyitozo igamije no gukora neza mu kongera ubumenyi bw'abaturage ku cyorezo kandi kenshi no kugenzura no kunoza uburyo bwo gusubiza abaturage.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na virusi nshya SARS-CoV-2 cyatangiye mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019.
Mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo ku isi.
Kubera ko virusi isa cyane na SARS-CoV kandi ibimenyetso bikaba bisa cyane hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatumye SARS igaruka.
Icyakora, hari itandukaniro rikomeye hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, rikenewe mu kugabanya icyorezo no kuvura abarwayi.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane abagabo kurusha abakiri bato n'abasaza kurusha abagore, kandi ubukana n'urupfu mu bantu bakuze na byo ni byinshi kurusha mu rubyiruko.
Imfu za SARS ziruta iz' COVID-19 (10.91% vs 1.44%).
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakwirakwiza virusi nubwo nta bimenyetso bagaragaza, mu gihe abarwayi ba SARS bakunze kubikora iyo barwaye cyane, bigatuma bigoye cyane kugabanya ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 kurusha SARS.
Ibi bisobanuye mu rugero runaka impamvu SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira ku buryo bwihuse kandi bwimbitse kurusha SARS-CoV.
Ibizamini bya RNA bisanzwe bya SARS-CoV-2 bishobora kugaragaza ko nta ndwara ya COVID-19 mu barwayi bamwe na bamwe.
Ku rundi ruhande, abarwayi bakize bashobora kongera kugaragaza virusi.
Ibi byavuye mu bushakashatsi byongereye cyane ibyago byo gukwirakwira kwa virusi.
Nubwo ubushakashatsi kuri COVID-19 bwateye imbere cyane, hari ibibazo byinshi bikomeye bikiri gukemuka, ari byo:
SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse he?
Nubwo hari ihure ry'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo rya 96% hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na CoV ebyiri zisa na SARS z'ikinyugunyugu, ntitwavuga ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse ku gikinyugunyugu.
Umutungo usanzwe, reka tuvuge ko ari ubwoko ki bw'inyamaswa bwabaye hagati mu kwanduzanya virusi kuva ku birura bigera ku bantu?
Tutabonye igisubizo cya #1 na 2, ntidushobora guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo kandi gishobora kongera kubaho igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
Nubwo ibizamini by'imikorere ya molekile n'ibyigwa mu binyabuzima byagaragaje ko SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano na ACE2, ni gute virusi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umuyoboro w'umwuka, igakurikizaho impinduka z'indwara?
Ese virusi ishobora no kwifatanya n'utundi duce tw'umubiri dufite ACE2?
Nta bisubizo byumvikana kuri ibyo bibazo, ntidushobora kubona ibipimo byahise kandi byuzuye, cyangwa se imiti ikora neza.
Iki cyorezo kizakomeza kubaho igihe kingana iki?
Ni gute virusi ihinduka mu buryo bw'imiterere mu gihe cyo kwanduzanya mu bantu?
Ese izaba icyorezo ku isi, kigenda gifata indi ntera nk'icyorezo cya SARS, cyangwa kizakomeza kugaruka nk'ibicurane?
Ni ngombwa, ariko bishobora gufata igihe runaka kugira ngo umuntu abone ibisubizo by'ibyo bibazo ndetse n'ibindi byinshi.
Ariko kandi, uko igiciro cyaba kiri kose, nta kundi twabigenza uretse guhagarika icyorezo vuba na bwangu no gusubiza ubuzima bwacu mu buryo.
Inkomoko y'ibinyabuzima bya koronavirusi y'umuntu
Imyubakire n'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byatumye virusi za coronavirusi (CoVs) n'ibinyabuzima byanduza (harimo n'abantu) bigenda bihinduka mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu babiri bari bazi ko bafite virusi z'ubwandu bw'indwara zo mu bantu (HCoVs) zitera indwara zidakomeye nk'iz'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cya SARS na MERS byasimbuye burundu ibintu byose, byerekana ko HCoV ifite ubukana bukabije kandi bwica.
Ivuka rya SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa rwagati mu mpera za 2019 ryongeye gushyira CoVs ku karubanda kandi ritangaza abantu kubera ubwandu bwinshi ariko bugabanuka ugereranyije na mushiki wayo SARS-CoV.
Indwara ya HCoV ni indwara yandurira mu nyamaswa kandi gusobanukirwa inkomoko y'indwara ya HCoVs mu nyamaswa bizadufasha.
HCoVs nyinshi zakomotse ku birura, aho zitagira ubwandu.
Hari n'amakuru ajyanye n'ibinyabuzima byo mu nda bya intermédiaire bya HCoVs zimwe na zimwe.
Kumenya intungamubiri z'inyamaswa bifite ingaruka z'ibanze mu kwirinda indwara z'abantu.
Gusuzuma imikoranire ya CoV-nutrient mu nyamaswa nabyo bishobora gutanga ibisobanuro byingenzi ku ndwara ya CoV mu bantu.
Muri iyi raporo, twerekana uko amakuru y'ubu ku ndwara zirindwi za HCoVs ameze, twibanda ku mateka y'ubushakashatsi, hamwe n'ubwanduzi buturuka ku nyamaswa no ku bantu.
Icy'ingenzi, turagereranya kandi tugereranya HCoVs zitandukanye mu buryo bw'iterambere rya virusi n'ihindagurika ry'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo.
Muri iki cyiciro, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kivugwaho ko ari indwara ya CoV.
Byongeye kandi, byerekana ko ari ngombwa guhindura neza intungamubiri hamwe n'ingaruka zo gukura kwa virusi buhoro buhoro ku buremere bw'indwara.
Coronaviruses (CoVs) ni zo zigize umuryango wa Coronaviridae ugizwe n'itsinda ry'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe bw'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe bwa virusi za RNA z'uruhu rumwe, z'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe.
Izo virusi, zifite genome nini cyane iri hagati ya kilobases 26 na 32 muri virusi za RNA, zitiriwe CoVs kubera imiterere yazo isa n'iy'ikamba, ikorwa hakoreshejwe mikorosikopi ya elegitoron.
Mu buryo bw'imiterere, CoV zifite genome zitagira ibice bifite imiterere imwe.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya genome bigizwe n'ibice bibiri binini by'ibisobanuro (ORF1a na ORF1b) bihinduka pp1a na pp1ab bihindura polyproteine.
Poroteyine nyinshi zikorwaho ibindi kugira ngo zitange poroteyine 16 zitari iz'ubwubatsi zitwa nsp1~16.
Ibisigaye bya genome birimo ORFs ku maporoteyine yubwubatsi harimo spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) na nucleoproteins (N).
Poroteyine nyinshi z'ubufasha zihariye mu bwoko bw'ibinyabutabire na zo zanditswe n'ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoVs.
Bitewe n'impinduka mu mikoranire ya poroteyine, CoV igabanywa mu bisekuru bine (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), muri byo Beta-CoV ni yo ishoramari rya HCoVs kandi igabanyijemo ibice bine (A, B, C na D).
Ibihamya by'ibinyabuzima byerekana ko udusimba n'utunyoni ari byo byinshi mu bitanga ibinyabuzima bya alpha-CoVs na beta-CoVs, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zitanga ibinyabuzima bya gamma-CoVs na delta-CoVs.
Mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, CoVs zakomeje kurenga inzitizi z'ubwoko, zigeramo kuba zimwe mu ndwara z'ingenzi ku bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana abantu barindwi banduye virusi itera SIDA (HCoVs).
Muri byo harimo HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 alpha-CoVs.
Ibindi bitanu bya beta-CoVs birimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje nk'ibicurane na/cyangwa iseseme.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 nshya yamenyekanye, ni indwara ziteye indwara cyane, zitera indwara zikomeye zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi mu barwayi benshi cyane bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara z'ubuhumekero bukabije (ARDS) n'ibimenyetso bya hypertensive.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwitandukanyijwe n'imyanda yo mu mazuru y'abarwayi barwaye ibicurane mu myaka ya za 1960.
Kuva icyo gihe, hari ibindi bisobanuro byakusanyijwe binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse kuri HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bitera ibimenyetso byigenzura.
Mu by'ukuri, mbere y'uko SARS itangira, abantu benshi bemeraga ko HCoVs zanduye zidakunze guteza akaga.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byorezo byangiza cyane mu mateka ya none, cyanduza abantu barenga 8000, gifite igipimo cy'urupfu rw'abantu batarapimye kiri hafi 10%.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) cyateye icyorezo gikomeje kwibasira akarere ka Arabiya, n'ibindi bice by'isi.
2019 Novel HCoV (2019-nCoV), nyuma yiswe SARS-CoV-2, ni yo ntandaro y'icyorezo gikomeje cy'indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), kimaze guhitana ubuzima bw'abantu 3,120 no kwandura abantu barenga 91,000 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Inzogera z'umuburo zirumvikana kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kiri hafi.
HCoVs esheshatu zose zifite inkomoko mu nyamaswa, zaba iz'ibinyugunyugu, imbeba cyangwa inyamaswa zo mu ngo.
Ibihamya byinshi bishyigikira iterambere ryiyongeyeho ry'ama HCoVs yose kuva ku birura, aho virusi zihindutse neza kandi zitagira ubwandu, ariko zigaragaza itandukaniro rinini ry'imiterere.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateje ibibazo bikomeye mu buvuzi, mu bya siyansi, mu mibereho y'abaturage no mu by'umuco mu Bushinwa no ku isi.
Gushakisha inkomoko ya HCoVs mu nyamaswa bitanga uburyo bwo gusobanukirwa amateka kamere y'ubwandu, imbaraga zituma habaho ubwandu n'ibintu bituma habaho ubwandu.
Bishobora kuyobora cyangwa byorohereza ubushakashatsi ku ntungamubiri z'ibinyabuzima, interimeri n'izongera za SARS-CoV-2 zifite ingaruka zikomeye mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'ejo hazaza.
Muri iyi raporo, twerekana uko HCoVs ziterwa n'inyamaswa, uko zitwara abantu n'ibintu n'uko zandura.
By'umwihariko, twerekana kandi tuganira ku ngingo rusange ivuga ko virusi z'ababyeyi ba HCoVs zidakora indwara mu ntungamubiri z'umubiri wabyo, ariko zikaba zisigaye zangiza nyuma yo kwanduzanya mu bwoko bushya.
Tuzongera dusuzume imiterere y'ihindagurika rya HCoV aho ubwandu bwiyongera akenshi bugahwana n'igabanuka ry'ubwandu.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, ingaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 gikomeje kuganirwaho.
Imirambo ya CoVs yo mu nyamaswa yamenyekanye kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 30.
Mbere y'uko ubwoko bwa HCoV-229E bwitandukanywa bwa mbere n'imyanda y'imyanya y'amaraso y'abarwayi banduye ibicurane bisanzwe, CoV zitandukanye zatandukanyijwe n'inyamaswa nyinshi zanduye zirimo igifu, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n'imbwa.
Mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize, hamaze kumenyekana HCoVs zirindwi.
Igisobanuro kigufi ku mateka y'ubushakashatsi bwa HCoV (Imbonerahamwe ya 1) kizaba ari icy'ubumenyi kandi cyigisha.
HCoV-229E yavumbuwe bwa mbere mu 1966 mu nzira z'ubuhumekero z'abarwayi bafite ubwandu bw'umuhogo wo hejuru, nyuma yaho ihindurirwa imiterere ikura mu mibiri y'ibihaha bya WI-38.
Mu barwayi banduye HCoV-229E, ibimenyetso by'ibicurane birimo umutwe, gusuhererwa, kugira iseseme no kuribwa n'izuru byagaragaraga mu byiciro 10~20% by'abarwayi bafite umuriro n'umuhogo.
Nyuma mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yatandukanyijwe n'umuyoboro w'ingingo mu bwonko bw'imbeba yonsa amata.
Ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa HCoV-OC43 bisa n'ibyavuye ku cyorezo cya HCoV-229E, mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo bitandukanywa n'ibindi byorezo by'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nka virusi ya Infuenza A na rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi byogeye ku isi hose kandi birashoboka ko byanduzwa cyane mu gihe cy'itumba, hamwe n'ikirere cy'ubushyuhe.
Ubusanzwe, igihe cy'iterambere ry'izi virusi zombi kirenza icyumweru, gikurikirwa n'ibyumweru 2 by'indwara.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abakorerabushake, abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza banduye HCoV-229E bagize imbeho nke.
Abarwayi bake bafite ubumuga bwo kutabona bagaragaza indwara zikomeye zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi.
SARS, izwi kandi nka "Nymonia Atypical", ni icyorezo cya mbere cyandujwe na HCoV mu mateka y'abantu kandi cyatewe n'impamvu, HCoV ya gatatu yavumbuwe, SARS-CoV.
Umuntu wa mbere wanduye SARS ashobora kuba yaramenyekanye mu mpera za 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe icyorezo cya SARS cyakwirakwiraga mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane, habonetse abarwayi 8,096 hamwe n'abantu 774 bapfuye.
Uretse abafite ubwandu bwinshi, byatekerejwe ko hashobora kubaho kwiyongera kw'ibyago bibiri by'ibanze bitewe na buri muntu, hamwe n'igihe cyo gukura cy'iminsi 4 kugeza ku minsi 7 n'ingaruka zikomeye za virusi zigaragara ku munsi wa 10 w'indwara.
Abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'imbangukiragutabara, umutwe, umuriro, kugira iseseme n'ubukonje, bikurikirwa n'ububabare bwo guhumeka, inkorora n'ububabare bwo guhumeka.
Imyitozo yo gupima imikorere y'umubiri, lymphopenia, n'iyongerwa ry'imikorere y'umubiri ni bimwe mu bintu bisanzwe by'indwara ya SARS.
Ibyangiritse mu mubiri, gukwirakwira kw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'uruhu no kwiyongera kwa macrophages na byo bigaragara mu barwayi ba SARS.
Hafi 20-30% by'abarwayi nyuma yaho bakenera kwitabwaho cyane no guhumeka.
Usibye inzira y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, ingingo nyinshi zirimo urumogi, impyiko n'impyiko, akenshi zifite cyokoine, na zo zishobora kwandura muri ibi bihe bikomeye, bishobora guhitana cyane cyane abarwayi bafite ubumuga.
Virusi yatangiriye gutandukanywa n'umurwayi wavuye mu muryango we mu gupima ibihaha byabonetse, wavuye mu mujyi wa Guangzhou ajya muri Hong Kong.
Kuva icyo gihe, hakozwe imbaraga nyinshi mu bushakashatsi ku ndwara ya HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yatandukanyijwe n'umwana w'amezi 7 mu Buholandi mu mpera za 2004.
Mu ntangiriro, byagaragaraga ko byandura mu bana bato, abasaza n'abarwayi bafite ubumuga bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Indwara ziterwa na HCoV-NL63 zikunze kugaragara nk'ibicurane, conjunctivitis, umuriro, na bronchiolitis.
Mu bushakashatsi bwa kabiri bwigenga, basobanuye gutandukanya virusi imwe n'iy'umwana w'amezi 8 urwaye ibicurane mu mazuru mu Buholandi.
Nubwo byamenyekanye mu Buholandi, byamaze gukwirakwira ku isi hose.
Bivugwa ko HCoV-NL63 itera indwara zisanzwe z'ubuhumekero zigera kuri 4.7% kandi ko yibasira cyane mu mpeshyi, itumba no mu itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano n'indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'amahembe, izwi kandi nka Croup.
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yatandukanyijwe n'umugabo w'imyaka 71 wari waragiye mu bitaro muri Hong Kong arwaye amapfa na bronchiolitis.
Uretse indwara z'ubuhumekero n'ubuhumekero zisanzwe mu baturage, HCoV-HKU1 na yo yavuzwe ko ifitanye isano n'indwara zikomeye z'ibicurane.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 yagaragaye ku isi hose iteza indwara z'ubuhumekero z'ubwoko bworoheje.
Izi HCoVs zose uko ari enye zatoranyijwe mu miryango, zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe mu bantu kandi ntizishobora guhinduka ngo zitere indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu, nubwo habayeho impanuka ziturutse ku mpamvu zitazwi nk'uko byagenze mu buryo budasanzwe bw'ubwoko bwa HCoV-NL63, ubwandu bukabije bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bwo hasi buherutse kuvugwa mu Bushinwa.
Ubusanzwe, izo HCoV na zo ziba zidafite ubumara cyangwa indwara iyo zimaze kugira ubushobozi bwo kwanduzwa neza no gukomeza kwibeshaho mu bantu.
MERS-CoV yatangiriye gutandukanywa n'ibihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, wari waratewe na nimoniya ikaze n'impyiko zidakora neza.
Mu gihe abenshi mu barwayi bemejwe n'abashakashatsi baturuka mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, hari ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi na Tuniziya byatangaje ko hari abanduye biturutse mu mahanga, rimwe na rimwe bakwirakwira mu babyeyi babo.
Icyorezo cya kabiri cyabaye muri Koreya y'Epfo mu 2015 n'abantu 186 bamaze kwemezwa ko banduye.
Imyitozo ya MERS, irangwa na Pneumonia ikomeye igenda igenda, isa n'iyo SARS.
Bitandukanye na SARS, abarwayi benshi bafite MERS na bo bagira ibibazo by'impyiko zikomeye, ibyo bikaba byarabonetse gusa muri MERS mu ndwara ziterwa na HCoV.
Abarenga 30% mu barwayi bagaragaza ibimenyetso byo mu maraso nk'iseru no gusubiranamo.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, hari hamaze kumenyekana abanduye barenga 2500 bemejwe n'abashakashatsi, bafite igipimo cyo gupfa kiri hejuru cya 34.4%, bituma MERS-CoV iba imwe muri virusi zangiza cyane abantu.
Hagati y'ukwezi kwa 12 kugeza mu mpera za 2019, mu Bushinwa, mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, habonetse imbaga y'abarwayi ba pneumonie bafite ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero bwo hasi ziterwa na SARS-CoV-2 ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima bw'abaturage ku rwego mpuzamahanga, ndetse ryita n'indwara COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, hari abantu 90,053 bamaze kwemezwa ko banduye ku isi hose, hamwe n'umubare w'abanduye bapfa ku kigero cya 3.4%.
By'umwihariko, umubare w'abandura mu Bushinwa ni 4.2%, mu gihe hanze yawo ari 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 ituma indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye nk'iza SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zigaragara nk'iz'umuriro, inkorora n'ubuhumekero bubi.
Hari n'abarwayi bagaragaza igifu.
Pneumonia ni kimwe mu bimenyetso bikomeye kandi bishobora kwiyongera vuba cyane bigatuma umuntu agira ikibazo cy'ubuhumekero.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zisa cyane kubera guhuza kwa nucleotide nyinshi ku kigero cya 82%, zigaragara mu mashami atandukanye y'ibisekuru.
SARS-CoV-2 nta gushidikanya ko idateza indwara nyinshi, ariko ikwirakwira cyane kurusha SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Hari abarwayi batagira ibimenyetso banduye SARS-CoV-2 kandi bashobora kuba batuma ikwirakwira ku isi hose.
Kugereranya no kureba itandukaniro rya SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi HCoV esheshatu byagaragaje ibintu byinshi bihambaye bihuriyeho n'ubundi butandukaniro.
Icya mbere, igihe cyo kwandura n'igihe cy'imikorere ya HCoV birasa cyane.
Muri iyi ngingo, SARS-CoV-2 ikurikiza inzira imwe n'izindi HCoV esheshatu.
Icya kabiri, uburemere bw'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 ni nk'ubwa SARS-CoV na HCoVs zatoraguwe mu miryango ine (ni ukuvuga HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63).
Ku ruhande rumwe, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugaragaza ibimenyetso bisanzwe bigaragara mu gihe cy'ubwandu bwa HCoVs zatoraguwe n'abaturage, zirimo izidafite ibimenyetso, zidakomeye cyangwa zidafite ibimenyetso.
Ku rundi ruhande, hashobora kugaragara igice gito cy'ibipimo by'ibipimo bikomeye bya COVID-19, nk'uko bimeze ku banduye SARS-CoV, nubwo imibare ari nto cyane.
Icya gatatu, SARS-CoV-2 nayo iragaragazwa mu kwanduzanya ubwoko bwa HCoVs n'ubundi bwoko bwa SARS-CoVs.
Ku ruhande rumwe, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 burangana cyane n'ubwandu bwa HCoVs zigerwaho n'abaturage.
Ku rundi ruhande, biracyari ngombwa ko byemezwa niba ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugabanuka nyuma yo gutera imbere mu bantu nk'uko byagenze ku ndwara ya SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Amaherezo, kimwe n'izindi HCoV, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugaragara mu bimera byo mu mwijima.
Niba SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwizwa mu kanwa n'umuhogo igira uruhare rukomeye mu mimerere imwe n'imwe nk'iyo SARS-CoV, ibisigaye bizagaragazwa n'inyigo zizakorwa mu gihe kizaza.
