Mu Kuboza 2019, habayeho icyorezo cya 2019 Novel Coronavirus (2019-nCoV), ubu cyiswe coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) ku mugaragaro, kandi virusi yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yashyize COVID-19 ku rutonde rw'indwara z'ibyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryateguye amabwiriza yihuse yo gukorana kandi asohoka kumurongo ku itariki ya 06 Gashyantare 2020 mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi bwa gisirikare.
Kuva cyandikwa, cyagiye gitangazwa cyane.
Ariko kandi, menya ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi n'ubumenyi bwacu bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro, dushingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ibyavuye mu bikorwa byo kwa muganga; bityo rero, ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura na zo ziracyakorwa.
Urugero, hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 na 3 Werurwe 2020, Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abaturage y'Ubushinwa yasohoye amavugurura arindwi y'ingingo z'ingenzi mu mabwiriza yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) hamwe n'impinduka mu byerekeranye na zimwe mu ngingo.
Ubu hari igisubizo cyatanzwe na Zhou et al. ku mabwiriza yacu, batanze igitekerezo cyoroshye cyo gushyiraho ikimenyetso gishingiye ku buhanga bwabo mu buvuzi.
Ibikorwa byabo byongeyeho ibimenyetso bishya mu mabwiriza yacu kandi bitanga ibisobanuro byingenzi kuri iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Turashyigikira umurimo w'ingenzi bakora kandi turabashimira.
Ariko kandi, akazi kabo gakeneye kuvugururwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya y'ubuvuzi n'ubuvuzi bwa COVID-19 (igitabo cya karindwi cy'igerageza) n'inyigo ziherutse gukorwa.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu gitabo cya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo umuntu ashobore gukora isesengura ryimbitse kugira ngo yemeze ko ari umuntu ukekwaho indwara, bisaba ko ikintu kimwe cyo mu mateka y'icyorezo gihuzwa n'ibintu bibiri byo mu bimenyetso by'uburwayi, cyangwa ibintu bitatu byo mu bimenyetso by'uburwayi niba nta mateka y'icyorezo bigaragara:
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) Amateka y'ingendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu bice biyikikije, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho abantu banduye COVID-19 batangajwe mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (2) Amateka y'ubumenyingiro bw'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 (banyuzwe n'ibizamini bya nucleic acid); (3) Amateka y'ubumenyingiro bw'abarwayi bafite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu bice biyikikije, cyangwa abandi baturage aho COVID-19 yatangajwe mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (4) Amateka y'ubumenyingiro bw'abantu banduye mu matsinda y'abantu banduye (ubwandu ≥ 2 n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya mito nko mu rugo, mu biro, ku ishuri, n'ibindi mu byumweru 2 bishize).
Ibimenyetso byo kugenzura: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) bifite ibimenyetso bigaragaza ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) umubare w'amaraso yera yose ugaragaza ko mu ntangiriro ari asanzwe, yagabanutse cyangwa yagabanutse.
Gushakisha umuntu wemejwe ko arwaye bigomba kuba bishingiye ku muntu ukekwaho ubwandu cyangwa ibimenyetso bya seriyumu birimo ibi bikurikira: (1) igihe nyacyo cyo gupima PCR ku SARS-CoV-2 kigaragaza ko afite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu; (2) ikurikirane rya virusi yose igaragaza ko ifite ibimenyetso byinshi bihuza na koronavirusi zizwi; (3) gupima Serum igaragaza ko ifite ibimenyetso by'ubudahangarwa bwa IgM bwihariye kuri SARS-CoV-2 na IgG; cyangwa SARS-CoV-2-igaragaza ko IgG ifite ibimenyetso by'ubudahangarwa byavuye ku bundi budahangarwa ikajya ku bundi, cyangwa se imibare y'uburwayi yiyongera inshuro ≥ 4 mu gihe cy'uburwayi buhambaye ugereranyije n'icyiciro cy'indwara.
Dushobora kubona ko gupima PCR mugihe nyacyo kuri aside ya nucleic mu myuga y'ubuhumekero cyangwa ibipimo by'amaraso byongerewe mu gice cya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Kumenya indwara z'ibipimo by'amaraso byongerewe mu gice cya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) no mu gice cya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma mu gice cya karindwi, ibimenyetso bya seriyumu byongerewe.
Izi mpinduka zari zishingiye ku kazi gakomeje gukorwa n'abashakashatsi, bagerageza gushaka ibikoresho byiza byo kumenya aside ya nikeleyike byatuma habaho gusuzuma vuba, hamwe n'ibipimo by'ubuhumekero birimo ibipimo by'amaraso, byongereye ibisubizo by'ibipimo bitandukanye, kandi bishyigikira kuzana ibisubizo by'ubwirinzi bwihariye mu buryo bwemewe.
Byongeye kandi, hari ibimenyetso byinshi bitwibutsa ko tugomba kwitonda ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso bidasanzwe n'ibimenyetso bidasanzwe.
Ku bw'ibyo, urutonde rw'imikorere ya Zhou et al. rugomba kuvugururwa, kuko bashyize mu byiciro "ibyago biri hasi" umuntu udafite ibimenyetso byo kwa muganga.
