OMS isaba abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza kwambara udupfukamunwa gusa mu gihe bafite ibyago byinshi, nk'abita ku muntu ufite COVID-19, nubwo yemera ko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gukora ku maso.
Ibihugu byinshi byatangiye gushishikariza abantu muri rusange kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Muri Amerika, CDC itera inkunga kwambara udupfukamunwa tudafite imiti dukorwa mu myenda. Ubushinwa bwateye inkunga cyane cyane abantu basanzwe bafite ubuzima bwiza gukoresha udupfukamunwa dukoreshwa mu kwivuza, cyane cyane iyo bari mu biganiro bya hafi n'abandi bantu (metero 1 (ibirenge 3) cyangwa munsi yayo).
Hong Kong irasaba kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi mu gihe ukoresha uburyo bwo gutwara abantu cyangwa uba ahantu hari abantu benshi.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima muri Thailand barimo gushishikariza abantu gukora udupfukamunwa tw'imyenda mu ngo zabo no kuwuhanagura buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Czech na Slovakia bibuza abantu kujya mu ruhame batambaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa ngo bambare udupfukamunwa n'utwondo.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bagiye ahantu hahurira abantu benshi kugira ngo birinde n'abandi.
Leta ya Autriche yasabye abantu bose binjira mu iduka ry'ibyokurya kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Israel yasabye abaturage bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bagiye ahantu hahurira abantu benshi.
Kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, Taiwan, ikora udupfukamunwa tugera kuri miliyoni icumi ku munsi, yatangije itegeko ryo kwambara udupfukamunwa ku bantu bari mu modoka zitwara abagenzi mu mihanda ya gari ya moshi no muri bisi z'imihanda ya kure ku itariki ya 1 Mata.
Panama yasabye abantu kwambara udupfukamunwa igihe bari hanze, ndetse banatanga inama yo gukora udupfukamunwa twakozwe mu ngo ku bantu badashobora kugura udupfukamunwa.
Udupfukamunwa twakoreshejwe cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Malaysia na Singapore.
Kwitarura abantu (nanone byitwa kwitarura abantu ku mubiri) bikubiyemo ibikorwa byo kugenzura ubwandu bigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya guhura kwa bugufi hagati y'abantu.
Uburyo bwo kubikora ni nko gushyira abantu mu kato; kubuza abantu kujya mu mahanga; no gufunga amashuri, ahantu bakorera, ibibuga by'imikino, za sitade cyangwa ibigo by'ubucuruzi.
Abantu bashobora gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo gutandukanya abantu baguma mu rugo, bagabanya ingendo, bakirinda ahantu hari abantu benshi, bakoresha indamukanyo zitagaragara, kandi bakirinda abandi mu buryo bw'umubiri.
Ubu ibihugu byinshi birasaba cyangwa byasabye ko abantu baguma kure y'ahandi mu bice byugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Umubare munini w'abantu bagaragajwe n'inzego za leta z'Amerika n'imiryango y'ubuzima wagabanutse cyane, uva ku bantu 250 (niba nta bwandu bwa COVID-19 buzwi mu karere) ugera ku bantu 50, hanyuma ugera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwahagaritse iteraniro rusange ry'abantu barenze babiri. Abasaza n'abantu bafite indwara z'ibanze nk'igisukari, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso, n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya indwara bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye n'ibibazo kandi bagirwa inama na CDC yo kuguma mu rugo uko bishoboka kose mu turere dufite icyorezo cy'abaturage. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye guhindura ikoreshwa ry'ijambo "kwirinda" rihindurwa "kwirinda mu buryo bw'umubiri", kugira ngo byumvikane neza ko intego yo gushyikirana ari ukuganira ku mubiri, mu gihe gukomeza kuba ahantu hahurira abantu benshi cyangwa kure.
Gukoresha ijambo "kwirinda" byateje impamuro ko abantu bagomba kwihererana burundu aho gushishikarizwa guhura n'abandi binyuze mu bundi buryo. Hari inzego zimwe na zimwe zatanze amabwiriza y'ubuzima bw'imyororokere agomba gukoreshwa muri iki cyorezo.
Muri byo harimo inama yo kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu ubana nawe gusa, udashobora kugaragaza ibimenyetso bya virusi cyangwa ntayo.
Abantu basanzwemo COVID-19 n'abakekwaho ubwandu, basabwe kwicumbikira mu rugo.
Ibigo by'ubuzima byatanze amabwiriza arambuye ku bijyanye no kwitarura abantu mu buryo bukwiriye. Guverinoma nyinshi zategetse cyangwa zasabye ko abaturage bose batuye mu duce twatewe n'icyorezo bose bajya mu kato.
Amabwiriza akomeye cyane yo kwisanzura mu bantu bafite ibyago byinshi ni ayo mu matsinda afite ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bashobora kuba baragiranye isano n'umuntu wanduye COVID-19 kandi abantu baherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere karimo ubwandu bwagutse, basabwe kwiherera mu kato iminsi 14 uhereye igihe cyo kwisanzura bwa nyuma.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura icyorezo ni uguhagarika cyangwa guhashya, no kugabanya.
Gucumbikira abantu mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo bigamije gutahura abantu banduye, hamwe no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kugenzura ubwandu no gukingira kugira ngo bareke gukwirakwira.
Iyo bidashobotse guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara, imbaraga zijya mu cyiciro cyo kugabanya ikwirakwira: ingamba zigakorwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo no kugabanya ingaruka zayo ku buzima n'imibereho y'abaturage.
Uburyo bwo kugabanya no kugabanya burashobora guhuzwa icyarimwe.
Gutegeka bisaba ingamba z'icyorezo z'indengakamere, kugira ngo icyorezo kiveho ku buryo umubare w'ibanze w'abandura ugabanuka ugera kuri 1. Kimwe mu byo wakora mu gucunga icyorezo cy'indwara zandura ni ukugerageza kugabanya icyorezo, bizwi nko kugabanya icyorezo.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo kurambirwa mu buvuzi kandi bigatanga igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Ibipimo byo kwirinda bitari ibiyobyabwenge bishobora gucunga icyorezo birimo ingamba zo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko kugira isuku y'amaboko, kwambara agapfukamunwa no kwitarura abantu; ingamba zo kwirinda abaturage, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika gahunda z'iteraniro; uruhare rw'abaturage mu gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira ibyo bikorwa; ndetse n'ingamba zo kwirinda ibidukikije, nko gusukura ubuso. Ingamba zikomeye zo kurwanya icyorezo zashyizweho mu Bushinwa nyuma y'uko uburemere bw'icyorezo bugaragaye, nko gushyira mu kato imigi yose no gushyiraho ingamba zikomeye zo kugenzura ingendo.
Ibihugu bindi na byo byafashe ingamba zitandukanye zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangije igenzura ryinshi n'igenzurwa ry'aho umuntu ari, kandi itanga imiburo ku ngendo z'abantu banduye.
Singapore yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye biyemeje kwihererana kandi igafatira ibihano bikomeye abananirwa kubikora.
Taiwan yongereye umusaruro w'udupfukamunwa no guhana ubucuruzi bw'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Ingero z'u Bwongereza na Amerika zigaragaza ko hari imbogamizi zikomeye mu guhosha (kugabanya ariko kudasenya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kucyikumira (kuhindura iterambere ry'icyorezo).
Gushyiraho uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya indwara bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abahakwa kwivuza ku buryo bukabije ku kigero cya 2/3 n'abapfa ku kigero cya kimwe cya kabiri, ariko amaherezo abantu babarirwa mu magana barahitanwa n'ibyo bikorwa, kandi n'ubuvurane burangirika.
Gukumira bishobora guhabwa umwanya w'ibanze, ariko bigomba gukomeza kugeza igihe virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo rubonetse, niba ari ubwa mbere), bitabaye ibyo, guhererekanya kugaruka vuba biturutse ku koroherwa mu ngamba.
Gushyiraho ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo guhashya icyorezo bitera ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza.
Nta miti yihariye ya antiviral yemewe kuri COVID-19, ariko imbaraga zo guteza imbere harimo no kugerageza imiti ihari ziracyakorwa.
Kunywa imiti ya rubanda, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora gufasha kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere, imiti ya ogisijeni, uruvange rw'amaraso n'imiti yo guhumeka bishobora kuba ngombwa.
Imyanzuro ishobora kuba mibi kurushaho iyo umuntu akoresheje za siteroyi.
Imiti myinshi yamaze kwemererwa kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa n'ubwandu bw'indwara iri kugeragezwa kugira ngo ikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
Nk'uko OMS ibivuga, hari "imiti gakondo n'iy'iwacu" ishobora koroshya ibimenyetso biterwa na SARS-CoV-19.
Kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku bakeneye abarwayi ba COVID-19 no guhuza ubuvuzi, byasobanuwe na OMS nk'ingamba z'ibanze zo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ibiro bya ECDC na OMS by'akarere k'u Burayi byatanze amabwiriza yo kwimura ibikoresho ku bitaro no ku nzego z'ubuzima bw'ibanze ku rwego rw'abantu benshi, harimo: gushyira imbaraga mu bikorwa by'ubutabire mu gupima COVID-19, gusesa imikorere y'icyitegererezo igihe cyose bishoboka, gushyira mu kato abarwayi banduye COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi bababaye cyane binyuze mu guhugura abakozi no kongera umubare w'imashini zitanga umwuka n'ibitanda.
Hari ibitekerezo byinshi ku byerekeranye n'aho abarwayi ba mbere (bitwa ko ari abarwayi zero) bashobora kuba baraturutse.
Icyorezo cya mbere cya Coronavirus cyamenyekanye ku wa 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abandura coronavirus muri Hubei wagendaga wiyongera.
Benshi muri bo bari bafitanye isano n'isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Hunan, aho n'inyamaswa nzima zagurishwaga, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi yaturutse kuri kimwe muri ibyo biremwa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ko ari icyaturutse ku nyamaswa. Itsinda ry'abantu barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero itagira icyorezo, ryavumbuwe ku ya 26 Ukuboza kandi rivurwa n'umuganga Zhang Jixian wo mu bitaro by'intara ya Hubei, wabimenyesheje Wuhan Jiangnan CDC ku ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan, baburiye bagenzi babo ku bijyanye na "coronavirus isa na SARS".
Abapolisi baburiye abaganga umunani barimo Li Wenliang bashinjwa gukwirakwiza ibihuha, undi muganga I Feng arakanirwa n'abamurushaga.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan nyuma yaho yatanze itangazo rusange ku ya 31 Ukuboza, imenyesha WHO.
Mu ntangiriro za Mutarama, abategetsi b'ubuzima muri Wuhan babwiwe ko hari abantu benshi bafite indwara y'ubuhumekero itaramenyekana, bituma batangira gukora iperereza. Mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri hafi buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara z'Ubushinwa kubera urujya n'uruza rw'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa, kandi Wuhan ni ikigo cy'ingendo n'ihuriro rikomeye ry'ingendo z'indarayi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwanditse abantu bashya bagera ku 140 ku munsi, barimo babiri i Beijing n'umwe i Shenzhen.
Imibare yemewe nyuma y'aho yerekana ko abantu 6,174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso kugeza ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020. Kugeza ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yarenze Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani ku mubare munini w'abanduye ku isi. Kugeza ku ya 9 Mata 2020, abantu barenga miliyoni 1.61 baramaze kumenyekana ku isi hose; abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye kandi abantu barenga 364,000 bakize.
Ibihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200 bifite nibura umuntu umwe urwaye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije u Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byahagaritse urujya n'uruza rw'abantu kandi bishyiraho imipaka.
Ibisubizo by'igihugu birimo ingamba zo kugabanya abantu nk'igitaraganya (zwi nka Guma mu rugo, itegeko ryo kwihisha mu nzu, cyangwa gufunga). Ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300 muri Amerika cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 muri Filipine bari mu gufunga, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo bari mu gufunga, n'abantu miliyari 1.3 mu Buhinde bari mu gufunga.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga, nyuma y'iminsi ibiri biyongera bagera kuri miliyari 2.6 - ni ukuvuga hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 yavumbuwe i Wuhan ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019; raporo idafite ibimenyetso byemeza ko umuntu wa mbere yanduye yabaye ku ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Umuganga Zhang Jixian yabonye umugwi w'abantu barwaye indwara ya Pneumonia ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, nyuma yaho ibitaro bye byabwiye Wuhan Jiangnan CDC ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019, isuzuma ry'ibanze ry'ibinyabuzima mu bipimo by'umurwayi ryerekanye ko hari coronavirus isa na SARS.
Itangazo ry'abaturage ryatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umujyi wa Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza.
WHO yabimenyeshejwe uwo munsi.
Nyuma y'aya makuru, abapolisi bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan baburiye abaganga ko batagomba "kwirakwiza ibihuha" ku cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'Ubushinwa yari yabanje kuvuga ko nta "gihamya isobanutse" y'ubwandu bw'umuntu ku wundi.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukaze bwo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi, bwiswe "intambara y'abaturage" na Xi Jinping, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti b'Ubushinwa.
Byasobanuwe ko ari "igikorwa cy'igenzura cya mbere mu mateka y'abantu", ku ya 23 Mutarama, muri Wuhan hatangajwe akarere k'igenzura kugira ngo hamenyekane ko nta bantu bashobora kugenda, kageze mu mijyi 15 yose muri Hubei, hagaragaramo abantu miliyoni 57.
Imodoka z'abantu ku giti cyabo zari zarabuzanyijwe mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya w'Abashinwa (ku ya 25 Mutarama) byahagaritswe mu duce twinshi.
Abategetsi kandi batangaje ko hari hagiye kubakwa ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Hoshensen, byuzuye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hari ikindi bitaro cyitiriwe Leichensson cyubatswe kugira ngo kijye kivura abarwayi benshi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 muri Wuhan nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro na stade, biba ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, guverinoma yashyizeho ingamba zinyuranye zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga amatangazo yubuzima ku bagenzi no kwagura ikiruhuko cya Spring Festival.
Amashuri makuru n'amashuri yisumbuye yo hirya no hino mu gihugu na yo yari yafunzwe.
Intara za Hong Kong na Macao zashyizeho ingamba nyinshi, cyane cyane ku bijyanye n'amashuri n'amashuri makuru.
Ingamba zo gukora kure zashyizwe mu bice byinshi by'Ubushinwa.
Ingendo zari zibuzanyijwe mu gihugu no hanze ya Hubei.
Ubwoko bw'ingendo z'abantu benshi bwarahindutse, kandi inzu ndangamurage zo hirya no hino mu Bushinwa zarafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Imihanda y'abantu mu mijyi myinshi yari ifunze, kandi abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bagereranywa ko bahuye n'uburyo bumwe bwo guhagarika hanze. Nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo kigera ku rwego rw'isi yose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira "kuza" kwa virusi ivuye mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho gahunda y'iminsi 14 yo kwisanzura ku bantu bose b'abanyamahanga binjira mu mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, mu minsi itanu ishize, mu Bushinwa bw'ibanze hatanzwe umuntu umwe gusa wanduye, muri iki gihe akaba yari umushoferi wari uturutse i Istanbul agaruka i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Premier w'Ubushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bwanduye mu gihugu ryahise rihagarikwa kandi ko icyorezo cyigaruriwe mu Bushinwa.
Ingendo mu gihugu cya Hubei, uretse i Wuhan, zaragabanyijwe ku munsi umwe nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho Guma mu Rugo. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bafite visa cyangwa ibyangombwa by'uburaro bizahagarikwa guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, nta n'amakuru yihariye y'igihe iyo politiki izavaho.
Abantu bifuza kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba visa muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsili z'Ubushinwa.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije gufungura ubucuruzi n'inganda ku ya 30 Werurwe kandi itanga ingamba zo kongera kuzamura ubukungu bw'ubucuruzi. Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje umunsi w'icyunamo, ku itariki ya 4 Mata saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo, hatangira umunota wa gatatu w'agacerere ku rwego rw'igihugu, mu gihe cya Qingming Festival, nubwo guverinoma y'ibanze yasabye imiryango guha icyubahiro kuri interineti, ikurikiza intera y'umubiri mu kwirinda icyorezo gishya cya COVID-19.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe mu Bushinwa kiza muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ubuzima cyanditse ko habaye ukwiyongera gutangaje mu barwayi bemejwe ku ya 20 Gashyantare, bifitanye isano n'imbaga y'abantu benshi i Daegu, mu idini rishya rizwi nka Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abayoboke ba Shincheo baje i Daegu baturutse i Wuhan, bashidikanyaga ku nkomoko y'icyo cyorezo.
Kugeza ku ya 22 Gashyantare, 1,261 cyangwa hafi 13% by'abayoboke 9,336 b'Itorero batangaje ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje icyiciro cyo hejuru cy'umuburo ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Koreya yatangaje ko imaze kugira abarwayi barenga 2,000, ku ya 29 Gashyantare biyongera bagera ku 3,150.
Inzego zose z'igisirikare cya Koreya y'Epfo zashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'ibizamini byemeje ko abasirikare batatu banduye.
Porogaramu z'indege na zo zarahuye n'ingaruka kandi zarahindutse. Porogaramu yatanzwe na Koreya y'Epfo yari ifashwe nk'iyari nini kandi iteguwe neza ku isi mu gupima abaturage kuri virusi no gutandukanya abantu banduye, ndetse no kumenya no gushyira mu kato abo bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima bwagombaga kuba bugizwe no kwisuzumisha ibimenyetso by'abantu bashya bavuye mu bindi bihugu binyuze kuri porogaramu ya telefoni, gupima vuba virusi ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 20,000 ku munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'aho ari intsinzi mu kugenzura icyorezo nubwo nta mijyi yose yashyizwe mu kato. Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo watangiye ugabanyijwemo ibice ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yakiriye iki cyorezo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba kwirukanwa kwa Moon, bavuga ko leta yafashe nabi iki cyorezo, cyangwa bashima uko yabyifashemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo ifite umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byamenyeshejwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abanyamahanga bose bashya bazajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibitangazamakuru ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ibyifuzo by'ubufasha mu gupima virusi biturutse mu bihugu 121 bitandukanye.
Irani yatangaje ko ku ya 19 Gashyantare, muri Qom hari abantu babiri bapfuye bishwe na SARS-CoV-2 mu gihe abandi babiri bo muri icyo gihugu bapfuye nyuma yaho, nk'uko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi bw'Ubuvuzi yabitangaje.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo gufunga ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, imikino, n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, na za kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yatanze miliyari eshanu z'amanyarwanda yo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twatewe n'icyorezo yari ihari kandi ko abantu bonyine ari bo bari gushyirwa mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imigi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo urujya n'uruza rwinshi hagati y'imigi rwakomeje mbere y'umwaka mushya w'abaperesi wa Navroz.
Kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, insengero z'aba Shiite i Qom zari zifunguye ku bayoboke b'idini rya Islam. Muri Gashyantare, Iran yabaye ihuriro ry'ikwirakwizwa rya virusi nyuma y'Ubushinwa.
Hagati y'ibirego byo guhisha umubare w'abandura muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byashoboye kubona isano y'ibyago byabo na Irani kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye ushobora kuba ukabije cyane ugereranyije n'abanduye 388 bari baranditswe na leta ya Irani kugeza kuri uwo munsi.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe ku wa 3 Werurwe ubwo 23 mu bayigize 290 bageragezwaga bagasanga baranduye.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza ya Irani kurekura nta nkomyi abavugizi b'uburenganzira bw'ikiremwamuntu bafunzwe bazira imyigaragambyo y'amahoro no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zibikwiriye.
Yavuze ko ibigo byafunzwe, nk'ibigo by'ubwirinzi, bifite ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi, kandi bidafite ubuvuzi buhagije.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, umubare munini w'abapfuye mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 ba Irani n'abayobozi ba leta bapfuye bazize icyo cyorezo.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Iran yari irimo kugaragaza abantu bashya 50 buri saha, n'urupfu rushya buri minota icumi bitewe na coronavirus.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi wa OMS, ibipimo by'abanduye bishobora kuba bikubye inshuro eshanu ibyo muri Iran.
Byanavuzwe ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Iran bishobora kuba byarabangamiye ubushobozi bw'igihugu bwo kwitabira icyorezo cya virusi.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ushinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu bigabanywa ku bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Iran.
Icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo abakerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bageragezwaga bagasanga baranduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Ibibazo byatangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose ziva n'izituruka mu Bushinwa, ndetse igatangaza ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hatangiye icyiciro cy'abantu 16 bamaze kwemezwa ko banduye COVID-19 mu ntara ya Lombardy. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya rigenga ubutabera rigamije gukumira icyorezo, rivuga ko abantu barenga 50,000 bo mu mirenge 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani bashyizwe mu kato.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Mu bice byugarijwe n'icyorezo, kwinjira no gusohoka ntibizatanzwe.
Ku ya 4 Werurwe, Guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza zose zifunga burundu mu gihugu, kubera ko mu Butaliyani hapfuye abantu 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino y'umupira w'amaguru ya Serie A, yagombaga kuba nta bantu bayireba kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yasubitswe burundu mu gihe cy'ukwezi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yategetse ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bihagarikwa, uretse amaduka manini n'amafarumasi. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani cy'Abaganga b'Abaganga, Abarwayi, Abatabazi n'Abaforomo (SIAARTI) cyasohoye inama z'imyifatire y'ubuvuzi ku buryo bwo gutandukanya abarwayi bafite ibibazo bikomeye, bushobora gukoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwasize Ubushinwa mu bihugu bifite umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye bazize coronavirus nyuma yo gutangaza ko hari abantu 3,405 bapfuye bazize icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'igisirikare mu Butaliyani zifite ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari hamaze kuboneka abarwayi 128,948, hapfuye 15,887 kandi habonetse 21,815, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN yagaragaje ko kuba mu Butaliyani hari abaturage benshi bageze mu za bukuru kandi abantu bari bafite virusi icyo gihe bakaba batashoboraga gupimwa, bishobora kuba byaratumye hapfa abantu benshi.
Igisubizo cy'Ubwongereza kuri virusi cyabanje kugaragara nk'icyoroshye cyane mu bihugu byazahajwe, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, guverinoma y'Ubwongereza ntiyari yarashyizeho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gutandukanya abantu cyangwa ingamba zo gushyira abantu mu kato ku baturage bayo.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko leta yanenzwe kubera ko nta muvuduko n'imbaraga yari ifite mu gusubiza ibibazo by'abaturage. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yagiriye inama abantu kwirinda ingendo zose zidakenewe no guhura n'abandi, abasaba gukorera mu rugo aho bishoboka no kwirinda ahantu nko mu tubari, muri resitora no muri za sinema.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ibikorwaremezo byose by'imyidagaduro nk'amazu y'imyidagaduro na za siporo bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi yiyemeza kwishyura abakozi 80% by'umushahara wabo kugeza ku mafaranga 2,500 ku kwezi kugira ngo barwanye ubushomeri mu bibazo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda abantu babiri, abuza abantu benshi guteranira hamwe kandi agabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze ku bikorwa byitwa ko ari ngombwa.
Bitandukanye n'ingamba za mbere, izi ngamba zashyizweho na polisi binyuze mu gutanga amande no gutatanya imbaga.
Ibigo byinshi byategetswe gufunga uretse ibifatwa nk "ibikenewe", birimo supermarket, farumasi, banki, amaduka y'ibikoresho, sitasiyo za lisansi na gare.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, leta ya Washington yo mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika yemeje ko umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 yanduye, akaba yari avuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Inteko Rusange y'Ibikorwa bya Coronavirus yashinzwe ku ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima bw'abaturage, buhagarika kandi abagenzi bava mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara - ikigo cy'ubuzima rusange cya leta ya Amerika - cyatangaje ko cyakoze ibikoresho byacyo byo gupima.
Nubwo Amerika yabigenje ityo, yatangiye igerageza buhoro, bituma gutahura urugero nyakuri rw'icyorezo icyo gihe bigorana.
Ibigeragezo byabangamiwe n'ibikoresho byo gupima bidakora byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemerwa na leta muri Gashyantare ku bikoresho byo gupima bitari ibya leta (n'abarimu, ibigo n'ibitaro), no kugenzura ibipimo bibuza abantu kuzuza ibisabwa kugira ngo bageragezwe mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (nyuma yaho hagombaga gutegekwa umuganga).
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru The Washington Post cyatangaje ko muri Amerika hari hasigaye ibizamini 4,000.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hari hasigaye ibizamini 14,000.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Associated Press cyatangaje ko: "Abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso kandi bafite amabwiriza ya muganga, bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi yo gupimwa". Guverineri J. Inslee yatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere rwatangajwe muri leta ya Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare muri Amerika, igikorwa cyahise gikurikirwa n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi kugeza hagati muri Werurwe, amashuri yo hirya no hino mu gihugu yari yarasubitswe. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, itsinda ry'inzobere mu by'iby'indwara z'ibyorezo muri Imperial College London ryatanze inama ku buryo Amerika iteganya ingaruka za coronavirus nshya ku gihugu.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku Itegeko ry'Itegeko ry'Itegeko ry'Itegeko ryerekeye Itegurwa n'Ibisubizo bya Coronavirus, ryatanze miliyari $8.3 mu nkunga z'ibigo bya leta mu buryo bw'impanuka mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho amategeko abuza abakozi kujya mu mahanga, yahagaritse amakoraniro kandi atera inkunga abakozi gukora bava mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibihe by'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje iminsi 30 y'amabwiriza yo guhagarika ingendo mu Burayi bwose, uretse mu Bwongereza.
Bukeye bwaho, yagutse ibihano bigera no mu Bwongereza no muri Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ibihe by'ibiza ku rwego rw'igihugu, byatanze amafaranga ya leta kugira ngo iki cyorezo kiveho.
Guhera ku ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi bwahagaritse imirimo cyangwa bugabanya amasaha y'akazi muri Amerika yose mu kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyemejwe mu bihugu byose 50 n'Akarere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko mu mujyi wa New York hari abantu 10,700 banduye coronavirus, baruta umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, Guverineri yavuze ko gutandukanya abantu byagize icyo bigeraho, kuko imibare y'ibyumweru by'ibyorezo bya kabiri yagabanutse iva ku minsi 2.0 igera ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, muri New York City hari hamaze kuboneka abarwayi 32,308, kandi abantu 672 barapfuye bazize virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yatangaje ko imaze kugaragaza abarwayi benshi ba coronavirus kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Kugeza ku ya 8 Mata, Amerika yari imaze kugaragaza abarwayi 400,335 kandi hapfuye abantu 12,841.
Amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru avuga ko ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu kure kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa USNS Comfort bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1000 bwashyize ingashya i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, muri Amerika hapfuye abantu 884 bishwe na coronavirus mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Umubare w'abanduye muri leta ya New York warenze 100,000 ku ya 3 Mata. Ibiro bya White House byanenzwe kugenzura ubutumwa binyuze mu gupfobya akaga no kuyobora abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza imvugo n'ibitabo by'abantu ku mugaragaro bijyanye na virusi n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Uburyo Trump yakoresheje mu guhangana n'ikibazo, bwagiye buhinduka bushingiye ku mitekerereze mibi.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenze ko Amerika ishingiye ku bicuruzwa by'ingenzi biva mu Bushinwa, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bikenewe.
Isesengura ry'imiterere y'ingendo z'indege ryakoreshejwe mu gusesengura no guhanura ikwirakwira ry'ingendo, kandi ryatangajwe hagati ya Mutarama 2020 muri The Journal of Travel Medicine.
Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, na Taipei ni byo bihugu bya mbere byagize umubare munini w'abagenzi bavuye i Wuhan, hashingiwe ku makuru yo mu 2018 yatanzwe n'ishyirahamwe ry'ingendo z'indege ku isi (International Air Transport Association).
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe nk'ahantu hakunzwe cyane n'abantu baturuka i Wuhan.
Bali ni wo wavuzwe ko ufite ubushobozi buke mu mijyi 20 ikunzwe cyane mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya ari yo yavuzwe ko ifite ubushobozi bwinshi. Australia yasohoye gahunda yayo y'ubutabazi bwihuta kuri Novel Coronavirus (COVID-19) ku ya 7 Gashyantare.
Ibi bivuga ko hari byinshi bitaramenyekana kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga kugenzura imipaka no gutumanaho mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko habayeho ikibazo cy'umutekano muke mu buzima bw'abantu.
Kubera kugenzura neza uburyo bwo gutwara abantu n'ibintu mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye ko abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi bavanwa muri ako gace, ahanini binyuze mu ndege zitwaye abantu mu gihugu cyabo, zemejwe n'ubutegetsi bw'Ubushinwa.
Canada, Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailand ni byo bihugu bya mbere byatangiye gutegura guhungisha abaturage babyo.
Pakistan yavuze ko itazongera gucyura abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yakuye muri icyo gihugu Abanyabrezili 34 cyangwa abagize umuryango wabo, uretse Abapolisi bane, Umushina umwe n'Umuhinde.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhinde bavuye mu ndege muri Polonye, aho indege ya Bresil yahagaze, hanyuma igatangira urugendo igana muri Bresil.
Abaturage ba Burezili bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare hafi ya Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, abaturage 215 b'Abanyakanada (176 ku ndege ya mbere na 39 ku yindi yari yaragizweho ingendo na Leta ya Amerika) bakuwe i Wuhan bajya muri CFB Trenton, maze bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye abaturage 185 b'Abanyakanada yavuye i Wuhan igera muri CFB Trenton.
Ku ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, abategetsi ba Ositaraliya bakuye abaturage 277 babajyana mu kigo cyo gufungirwa ku kirwa cya Noheli, cyongeye kubakwa nk'ikigo cy'ihoberana, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Indege imwe yo muri Nouvelle Zelande yageze muri Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe baturutse muri Ositaraliya no mu karere ka Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cya gisirikare i Wangaparoa mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Amerika yatangaje ko igiye kuvana Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yageze i Trenton, Ontario, itwaye abagenzi 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bavuye mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, Guverinoma y'u Buhinde yatangiye kuvana abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari yaratangijwe na Guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo yafashe abaturage 112 b'Abanyafurika y'Epfo.
Mbere yo kugenda, abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragayeho ibimenyetso bya coronavirus, bagizwe abere kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago byo kwandura.
Abanyafurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ko nta bwandu bafite ni bo bonyine basubijwe mu gihugu.
Ibyavuye mu bizamini byatangaje ko abanyafurika y'Epfo bose batanduye, barimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abapilote, abakozi b'amahoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari muri iyo misiyo y'ubutabazi, bose bari mu kato nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda kandi bagashyirwa mu kato muri The Ranch Resort mu gihe cy'iminsi 14.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukuraho igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yavuze ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Iran) byoherereje ubufasha Ubushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bishyize hamwe kugira ngo bafashe kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byazahajwe na virusi, bivugwa ko itsinda rihuriweho mu karere ka Chicago ryohereje udupfukamunwa 50,000 twa N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Umuryango w'ubutabazi Direct Relief, ufatanyije na FedEx, wohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi, birimo utwenda tw'amaboko n'imyenda, ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union, binyuze mu ndege yihutirwa kugeza ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya WHO mu rwego rwo kurinda "abaturage bafite ibyago byinshi muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo", ndetse no gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku rukingo no kuvura.
Interaction yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare, ubwo Senateri Richard Gordon yoherezaga udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 muri Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapuru yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni i Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko izatangaza uturindantoki tw'ubuvuzi miliyoni 18 mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi birimo amasuti 10,000 ya Hazmat, na Amerika yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa kandi isezeranya inkunga y'amafaranga miliyoni 100 mu bufasha bw'inyongera ku bihugu byazahajwe. Nyuma y'uko ikibazo mu Bushinwa gisa n'icyahagaze neza, igihugu kirimo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu bitandukanye byazahajwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'u Burusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke mu Butaliyani kugira ngo bifashe guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1 by'ibipimo, udupfukamunwa tw'amaso miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro 60,000 yo kurinda Addis Ababa, Ethiopia, kugira ngo bitangirwe n'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 na ventilateri 5 muri Panama.
Ma kandi yatanze imfashanyo z'ubuvuzi muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Czech byatangaje impungenge zabyo ku masike n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yasubije ibikoresho 58,000 by'igerageza bya Coronavirus byakozwe n'Ubushinwa bifite igipimo cy'ubwiru cya 30% gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwasubije udupfukamunwa 600,000 tw'Abashinwa twari dufite inenge.
U Bubiligi bwongeye gutumiza mu mahanga udupfukamunwa 100,000 tutakoreshwa, twitwaga ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga y'Ubushinwa yakiriwe neza mu bice bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubutabazi bw'ibanze ku bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye imbaraga z'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa mu gucunga no guhashya icyorezo.
OMS yavuze ko hari itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwaga ibanga ryatumye imihati yo gukumira no kugenzura ihagarara, n'ikibazo kiriho aho guverinoma nkuru "itanga amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo ikomeze guhangana n'ubwoba mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'ukwezi".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ibanze cyo gushyiraho itegeko ryo guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galya yagize ati "Ntabwo byanze bikunze byasabwe na OMS" ariko ni "ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cyo kwiyemeza kurwanya icyorezo aho cyibasiwe cyane" kandi cyitwa "kitari cyarigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi bw'ubuzima rusange bw'ihungabana mpuzamahanga (PHEIC) nyuma yo kwemezwa kw'ubwandu bw'abantu ku bantu hanze y'Ubushinwa no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'ibindi bibazo, ari nacyo cya gatandatu PHEIC kuva ingamba za mbere zashyizweho mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cyo mu 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC yatewe n "ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abifite ubukungu buciriritse bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza.
Mu gusubiza ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'ibihano byo gutembera, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zibuza ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "WHO idashishikariza kugabanya ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu rwego rwo kwitegura mu buryo bwa giteganyo mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, ivuga ko hakenewe gufashwa ibihugu "bitari bifite uburyo bwo gutahura abantu banduye virusi, nubwo yari igiye kugaragara".
Mu bindi bitangazo, Tedros yatangaje ko "turi abanyembaraga gusa nk'urungano rwacu rufite intege nke" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "kwishora mu bikorwa uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura byinshi nyuma". Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru yashyizeho COVID-19 nk'izina ry'indwara.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, Antonio Guterres, yemeye gutanga "imbaraga z'umuryango w'abibumbye wose mu guhangana".
Ingaruka zabaye uko hashyizweho itsinda rya ONU rishinzwe gucunga ibibazo, rihuza ibisubizo bya ONU yose, bizabafasha "kwita ku bisubizo by'ubuzima, mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gukoresha ubumenyi bwabo mu guhangana n'ingaruka zikomeye z'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere by'icyorezo", nk'uko WHO ibivuga.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'intumwa zihuriweho na WHO riyobowe n'Ubushinwa, ryatumiwe mu Bushinwa gusura ako karere mu rwego rwo gutanga amakuru y'ibanze ku bahanga mpuzamahanga na WHO, kugira ngo barebe "uburemere n'ubwandu bw'indwara" no "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza ku rwego rw'intara n'akarere, harimo n'imiyoborere y'imijyi n'imidugudu", bifashishije inama n'inama n'inama n'ibigo bikomeye byo ku rwego rw'igihugu, kugira ngo bifashe mu gucunga igihugu. Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, WHO yatangaje ko "isi igomba gukora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo yitegure icyorezo cya coronavirus", ivuga ko nubwo byaba hakiri kare cyane kuvuga ko cyateye, ibihugu bigomba gukomeza "kwitegura".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo kiri gutera imbere muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'ingabo z'imirimo ihuriweho kugira ngo bigenzure uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ku isi kizafatwa nk'icy'ibanze kuva ku "gipimo cyo hejuru" kugera ku "kibije cyane", kikaba ari cyo cyiciro cyo hejuru cyo kuba maso no gusuzuma ibyago.
Umuyobozi w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, Mike Ryan, mu itangazo yatanze, yaburiye ko "iki ari ikigeragezo kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: igihe kirageze cyo gukanguka".
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba igiye kuza kandi mugomba kwitegura", asaba ko ingamba nziza zo guhangana nazo zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi cyane".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko imibare iriho ubu idashobora kwemeza inzego z'ubuzima bw'abaturage gutangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza bene ibyo bivuze ko "tuba twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azahura n'iyo virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi mukuru yavuze ko OMS "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'urugero rubi rw'ikwirakwira n'uburemere ndetse n'urwego rubi rwo kudakora". OMS yakoreweho ibihano bikomeye kubera imyitwarire mibi y'icyorezo, harimo gutinda gutangaza ibura ry'ubuzima rusange no gushyira virusi mu byiciro nk'icyorezo.
Icyo cyemezo cyashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 kugeza ku ya 6 Mata, kirimo n'icyifuzo cyo kwegura kwa Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye zishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu zasabye ko uburenganzira bwa buri muntu bwose bwubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gufashwa mu kurokora ubuzima kandi ko ari inshingano za Leta.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura amikoro cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba na rimwe gukoreshwa nk'impamvu yo kurobanura ku butoni itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bemeje ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima bwiza, harimo abafite ubumuga, amatsinda y'abafite ubumuga, abageze mu za bukuru, abavuye mu byabo, abatagira aho baba, abari mu bukene bukabije, abari mu kato, ndetse n'impunzi n'andi matsinda atarasobanuwe akeneye ubufasha bwa Leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga itegamiye kuri leta irimo gukemura ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage z'ikibazo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubutwererane mu by'Ubukungu n'Iterambere watangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru mu gihe gikwiriye kandi arambuye, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama ku bitekerezo by'ingamba mu bihugu byo ku isi.
Kuva ku ngamba kugeza ku gukomeza uburyo bw'ubuzima, ndetse no ku bukungu bw'isi kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka zo guhagarika ingendo no kugabanya ingendo, ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga kirimo urukurikirane rw'ingamba z'igihugu, kandi kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku bindi no koroshya igisubizo cy'isi yose ku kibazo cya coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe cyane n'Amerika, Michael Gove, Minisitiri w'Ubwongereza ushinzwe ibiro bya Kabine, na Eduardo Bolsonaro, umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili, Jair Bolsonaro, kubera uburyo yakemuye icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei.
Abategetsi benshi bo mu rwego rw'intara bo mu ishyaka rya Komini y'Ubushinwa (CPC) birukanywe kubera guhangana n'imihati yo gushyira abantu mu kato mu Burasirazuba bw'u Bushinwa, mu rwego rwo kugaragaza ko batishimiye uko inzego za politiki zitabye icyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo batekereza ko iyi ntambwe yari igamije kurinda Xi Jinping, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa, uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bashyigikira ko COVID-19 yakomotse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubutegetsi bwa Donald Trump bwa Amerika bwise coronavirus "Virus y'Abashinwa" cyangwa "Virus ya Wuhan", buvuga ko "uburyo bwo kugenzura" Ubushinwa "bwahinduye virusi ubu ikaba icyorezo ku isi", bamwe mu banenga bavuga ko ari amacakubiri ashingiye ku moko kandi "atuma ubutegetsi bwe budashobora guhashya iki cyorezo".
Ikinyamakuru The Daily Beast cyabonye telegrafe ya leta ya Amerika igaragaza ko hari ikoranabuhanga ryihishe inyuma y'inama y'umutekano w'igihugu, ivuga ko "byose byerekeye Ubushinwa".
Turasabwa kugerageza gutangaza ubu butumwa mu buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose, harimo inama y'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo. "Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko imbaraga z'Ubushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byugarijwe na virusi ari igice cy'imikorere yo guteza imbere uruhare rw'isi.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga muri EU, Josep Borrell, yaburiye ko "hari igice cya politiki kirimo guharanira kugira ingaruka binyuze mu guhinduranya no 'politiki y'ubworoherane.'"
Borrell yongeyeho ko "Ubushinwa bukomeje gutangaza ubutumwa ko, bitandukanye na Amerika, ari umufatanyabikorwa ufite inshingano kandi wizewe".
Ubushinwa bwasabye kandi Amerika gukuraho ibihano ku bihugu bya Syria, Venezuela na Iran, byombi bivugwa ko byatanze imfashanyo.
Impano ya Jack Ma y'udupfukamunwa 100,000 yagenewe Cuba yahagaritswe n'ibihano bya Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Amerika na bo bashinjwa ko bahindura inkunga bageneye ibindi bihugu bayihindurira igihugu cyabo.
Kandi hari ibindi bihugu by'amahanga birimo Ubudage, Autriche n'Ubusuwisi, Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani, byagiye bivuguruza ku bijyanye n'udupfukamunwa.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe ibyuma bihumanya amagana byari bigenewe Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko EU idafite ubumwe n'Ubutaliyani bwatewe na coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, Ambasaderi w'u Butaliyani mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, yagize ati "Ubushinwa ni bwo bwonyine bwagize icyo buvuga ku buryo bw'impande zombi.
Nta gushidikanya, ibyo si ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubumwe bw'i Burayi".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma y'ikiganiro cya telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Butaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yateganyije kohereza abaganga b'ingabo, imodoka zihariye zo guhumanya indwara n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu ngabo z'u Burusiya.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo "isoko ya politiki yo ku rwego rwo hejuru" itazwi, kivuga ko 80 ku ijana by'ubufasha bw'Uburusiya "bwari imfabusa cyangwa nta kamaro kanini bwatanze mu Butaliyani".
Uyu mushinjacyaha yavuze ko u Burusiya bwakoze ibikorwa byo gushimagiza "ku rwego rwa politiki n'ibya dipolomasi".
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, n'umushikiranganji w'ububanyi n'amahanga w'Ubutaliyani, Luigi Di Meo, bahakanye ibyo bitangazamakuru kandi barashimira.
Uburusiya bwohereje imfashanyo y'ubuvuzi muri Amerika mu ndege itwara imizigo.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "mu gihe [Putin] aha inkunga bagenzi be bo muri Amerika, yemera ko igihe abakora ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho byo mu rwego rwa magendu bo muri Amerika bazongera umusaruro, bazaba bashobora no kwishyura igihe bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO "Defender 2020", imyitozo ikomeye cyane ya NATO nyuma y'iherezo ry'intambara y'ubutita mu Budage, Polonye, na Baltic, izaba ku rwego rwo hasi.
Umunyamabanga mukuru ushinzwe kugabanya intwaro za kirimbuzi, Kate Hudson, yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 agira ati "mu bibazo by'ubuzima rusange biriho, ntabwo byangiza ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'iburayi gusa, ahubwo binashyira mu kaga abatuye mu bihugu biyijyamo aho bakorera". Leta ya Irani yagezweho cyane n'iyi virusi, harimo abanyamuryango ba paruwasi bagera kuri mirongo ibiri banduye, hamwe n'abandi bantu cumi na batanu b'ubu cyangwa bahoze mu bya politiki.
Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yandikiye abayobozi b'isi ibaruwa y'umugaragaro ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020 asaba ubufasha, avuga ko igihugu cye kirimo guhangana no kurwanya icyorezo kubera kutagira amahirwe yo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga nk'ingaruka z'ibihano bya Amerika kuri Iran. Iki cyorezo cyatumye Amerika isaba ibihugu bikize gufata politiki z'imibereho myiza kimwe n'ibindi bihugu bikize, harimo ubuvuzi busanzwe, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango uhembwa, n'amafaranga menshi yo gushyigikira ubuzima rusange.
Abasesengura politiki bavuze ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku bushobozi bwa Donald Trump bwo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya Perezida yo mu 2020. Imishyikirano ya dipolomasi hagati y'Ubuyapani na Koreya y'Epfo yangiritse kubera icyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati y'igenzura idakwiriye kandi idakora" y'Ubuyapani ubwo Ubuyapani bwatangazaga ko umuntu wese uzava muri Koreya y'Epfo azajya mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri ahantu hateganyijwe na leta.
Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo wari waratangiye kwicamo ibice kubera uko Perezida Moon Jae - in yabyakiriye.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba kwirukanwa kwa Moon, bavuga ko leta yafashe nabi icyorezo, cyangwa bashima uko yabyitwayemo. Iki cyorezo cyatumye ibihugu byemera amategeko y'ibihe bidasanzwe mu rwego rwo guhangana nacyo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bagaragaje impungenge ko bishobora gufasha guverinoma gushimangira ububasha bwazo.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yayo yatoye yemerera minisitiri w'intebe, Viktor Orban gutegeka igihe kitarondoreka, ihagarika amatora hamwe n'inteko ishinga amategeko kandi ihana abantu bafatwa bakwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma kubijyanye no guhangana na virusi n'ibibazo no gukwirakwiza amakuru atari yo kuri guverinoma.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatewe n'ingero nyinshi z'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa, biturutse ku ikoreshwa ry'ibikoresho byo kurwanya icyorezo ku isi, kugura ibintu biterwa n'ubwoba, no guhungabanya ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze umuburo ku bijyanye n'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi kubera ko abakiriya bifuza cyane kandi abaguzi batabifitiye ubushobozi.
Mu bice byinshi, habayeho kugura ibintu biterwa n'ubwoba, bituma ibicuruzwa by'ibanze nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi yo mu macupa bigabanuka, bituma ibicuruzwa bigabanuka.
Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga mu buryo bwihariye cyahawe umuburo ku bijyanye n'ibihe byatinze byo gutwara ibicuruzwa bya elegitoroniki.
Dukurikije umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, ibisabwa mu bikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite byiyongereye inshuro 100.
Ibyo byateje kuzamuka kw'ibiciro by'ibisanzwe bikubye inshuro 20 kandi bituma ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi bidatangazwa mu gihe cy'amezi ane kugeza kuri atandatu.
Byatumye ku isi hose habaho ubukene bw'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyawe, WHO ikaba yarabuririye ko bishobora gushyira mu kaga abakozi b'ubuzima.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cyatumye abacuruzi ba Daigu babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Iki gikorwa cyatumye habaho ubukene bw'imiti y'abana mu maduka manini hanyuma ihagarikwa na leta ya Ositaraliya. Nubwo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan hari umubare munini w'abanduye COVID-19 kandi hakenewe ibiribwa byinshi, uturere twombi turimo guhangana n'ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zafashwe n'Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ubucuruzi bw'ibikoresho by'ingenzi n'ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko, zagize ingaruka nziza, zivanaho ibura ry'ibiribwa ryari ryitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Ubutaliyani bw'amajyaruguru ntibwigeze bubona igabanuka rikomeye mu bihingwa by'ingenzi, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera nk'uko byemejwe n'abahagarariye inganda.
Mu mujyi wa Wuhan, ibigega by'ibiribwa byuzuye byarebwe by'agateganyo gusa, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa basohoye ibigega by'inyama z'inshukeri kugira ngo abaturage babone imirire ikwiye.
Amategeko nk'ayo yo mu Butaliyani asaba abahinzi b'ibiribwa kubika ibicuruzwa byabo mu gihe habaye ibyago nk'ibyo.
U Bushinwa bwumviswe ingaruka z'ubukungu bw'isi: Nk'uko raporo y'itangazamakuru yo ku ya 16 Werurwe ibigaragaza, ingamba za leta zo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi, n'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bwagabanutseho 20.5%, byateje ibibazo bikomeye ubukungu bw'u Bushinwa mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa bukomeye ari ubukungu bukomeye n'ikigo cy'inganda, icyorezo cya virusi cyafashwe nk'icyateje akaga gakomeye ku bukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demaris wo mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubukungu cya Economist Intelligence Unit, yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza guhindagurika kugeza igihe habonetse igishushanyo cyiza cy'ingaruka zishoboka.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu bahanga mu by'inganda batangaje ko ingaruka z'icyorezo ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kuba zikomeye kurusha iz'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Impinduka y'igiciro cya miliyari $300+ ku muyoboro w'ibikoresho ku isi ishobora kumara imyaka ibiri, nk'uko byemejwe n'impuguke yo muri Kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis.
Ishyirahamwe ry'ibihugu by'ibihinguranya peteroli (OPEC) ryavuze ko "ryadohotse" nyuma yo kugwa kw'ibiciro by'ibikomoka kuri peteroli bitewe n'ibyifuzo bike biva mu Bushinwa.
Amasoko y'imigabane ku isi yaguye ku ya 24 Gashyantare kubera ukwiyongera gukomeye kw'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'u Bushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge zikomeje kwiyongera ku cyorezo cya coronavirus, imibare itandukanye y'imigabane ya Amerika, harimo NASDAQ-100, S&amp;P 500 Index, Dow Jones Industrial Average, yatangaje ko yagabanutse cyane kuva mu 2008, Dow igeze ku manota 1,191, ikaba ari yo yagabanutse cyane ku munsi umwe nyuma y'ibibazo by'imari byo mu 2007-08.
Ibipimo byose uko ari bitatu byagabanutseho 10% muri icyo cyumweru.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje igenzura ry'inguzanyo y'ubushobozi bw'ubushobozi bw'Ubushinwa, ariko ikomeza kwitega ko bizagenda nabi.
Ibicuruzwa byongeye kugwa bitewe n'impungenge za coronavirus, igabanuka rikomeye ryabaye ku ya 16 Werurwe.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko ubukungu buzagabanuka.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu, Mohamed Al-Erian, yashimye ingamba za Leta n'amabanki y'ibanze zafashwe mu gihe gikwiriye.
Banki nkuru z'ibihugu zagiye zisubiza vuba cyane kurusha uko zisubiza inyuma y'ibibazo by'imari byo mu 2008.
Ubukerarugendo ni kimwe mu bice byahuye cyane n'ibihano by'ingendo, gufunga ahantu hahurira abantu benshi harimo n'ibintu byo gutemberamo, inama za leta zo guhagarika ingendo zose ku isi.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko ingendo z'indege nyinshi zirimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Quantus zahagaritswe kubera ko hari ubushake buke, mu gihe Flybe, sosiyete y'indege y'akarere ka Leta zunze ubumwe z'Amerika, yaguye.
Ingaruka z'ibyo ku isosiyete y'amato ya Cruises ni zo za mbere z'izo ngaruka.
Ibigo byinshi by'amagare n'ibigo by'amato na byo byafunzwe.
Iki cyorezo gihuza n'igihe cy'ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa, ari cyo Chunyuan.
Imyinshi mu mikino, harimo n'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya, yahagaritswe na guverinoma z'igihugu n'iz'akarere, ndetse n'ibigo byigenga bifunga amaduka n'ahantu hahurira ba mukerarugendo nka Hong Kong Disneyland na Shanghai Disneyland.
Imikino myinshi y'umwaka mushya wa Lunar n'ahantu nyaburanga ho gutemberera mu mujyi wa Beijing byafunzwe kugira ngo hatagira abantu benshi bahurira hamwe, harimo n'umugi wabuzanyijwe n'ibirori by'urusengero gakondo.
Mu ntara 24, mu ntara 31, mu mirenge n'uturere 24 byo mu Bushinwa, abayobozi bongereye ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya kugeza ku ya 10 Gashyantare, bategeka ko ahantu henshi bakorera hatongera gufungura kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Ibi bice byiganjemo 80% bya GDP y'igihugu na 90% by'ibyoherezwa mu mahanga.
Hong Kong yongeye kuzamura urwego rwo guhangana n'indwara zandura kugeza ku rwego rwo hejuru kandi itangaza ibihe bidasanzwe, ifunga amashuri kugeza muri Werurwe kandi ihagarika kwizihiza umwaka mushya. Uruganda rw'ubucuruzi rwagize ingaruka ku isi hose, rugabanya amasaha y'ububiko cyangwa rufunga by'agateganyo.
Ingendo z'abacuruzi mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo zagabanutseho 40%.
Abacuruzi bo muri Amerika ya Ruguru n'iburasirazuba bwo hagati, babonye igabanuka rya 50-60%.
Abantu bagenda ku maguru mu mezi ya Werurwe, bagabanutseho 33-43% ugereranyije n'uko byari bimeze muri Gashyantare.
Abacuruzi bakorera mu maduka yo hirya no hino ku isi, bafashe ingamba zinyuranye, nko kongera isuku, gushyiraho ibyuma bifata ubushyuhe mu maduka bigenzura ubushyuhe bw'abaguzi, no guhagarika amakoraniro. Nk'uko Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe ubukungu muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo ibitangaza, ubukene buterwa n'icyorezo bushobora gutuma abantu bari hagati ya miliyoni 14 na 22 muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo baba mu bukene bukabije, batari kuba bari muri iyo mimerere iyo hataza kubaho icyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, mu gihe icyorezo cyari ku isonga mu mujyi wa Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 5 mu Bushinwa batakaje akazi kabo.
Abakozi benshi b'abimukira bo mu cyaro bagera kuri miliyoni 300 bo mu Bushinwa bafungiwe mu mazu mu ntara zo hagati mu gihugu cyangwa bafungiwe mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miliyoni 10 batakaje akazi kabo kandi basaba inkunga ya leta.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora kugabanya imirimo miliyoni 47 muri Amerika kandi umubare w'abashomeri ushobora kumanukaho 32% nk'uko byemejwe na Banki y'Igihugu y'Igihugu ya St. Louis. Abakozi b'abimukira babarirwa muri za miriyoni bagiye mu bushomeri (bishyurwa binyuze mu mishahara ya buri munsi) kubera gufunga mu Buhinde. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo Angus Read bwerekanye ko 44% by'imiryango yo muri Kanada yahuye n'ubushomeri bw'uburyo runaka.
Mu gice cya kabiri cy'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, abakozi b'Abafaransa miliyoni 4 basabye inyungu z'ubushomeri bw'agateganyo naho abakozi b'Abongereza miliyoni 1 basabye inguzanyo rusange. Amashyirahamwe agera kuri miliyoni imwe n'igice mu Budage yohereje abakozi bayo mu mishinga y'akazi y'igihe gito ishyigikiwe na leta yitwa Kurzarbet.
Ubufaransa n'Ubwongereza byashyize mu bikorwa gahunda y'indishyi z'akazi k'igihe gito yo mu Budage.
Urwego rw'ubuhanzi n'umurage w'umuco rwarahuye cyane n'icyorezo, bigira ingaruka ku mikorere y'imiryango ku isi, ndetse n'abantu bakora akazi no kwikorera ku giti cyabo.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuhanzi n'umuco yashyizeho imihati yo gukomeza inshingano zayo (benshi bishyigikiwe n'abaturage) zo kugeza ku baturage umurage w'umuco, kubungabunga umutekano w'abakozi n'abaturage no gushyigikira abahanzi aho bishoboka.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, hirya no hino ku isi no mu bihugu bitandukanye, inzu ndangamurage, ibitabo, ibibanza by'imyidagaduro, n'ibindi bigo by'umuco byari byarafunzwe igihe kitarondoreka, hamwe n'imurikagurisha ryabyo, imiterere n'imyidagaduro byahagaritswe cyangwa byigijwe inyuma.
Mu rwego rwo gusubiza, hakozwe ingufu nyinshi mu gutanga serivisi zindi binyuze mu buryo bwa digitale. Ikindi cyorezo giherutse kwiyongera ni ukuhagarika imirimo y'idini, imikino ikomeye, n'andi materaniro mbonezamubano, nk'ibirori by'umuziki n'amakoraniro y'ikoranabuhanga n'imideli.
Ikigo cya Vatican cyatangaje ko imihango yo kwibuka icyumweru gitagatifu i Roma, iba mu cyumweru cya nyuma cy'icyumweru cy'icyunamo cya Gikristo cya Lenti, yahagaritswe.
Amatorero menshi y'abapiskopi-akarere yasabye abakristu bageze mu za bukuru kuguma mu rugo aho kujya mu materaniro ku Cyumweru; amadini amwe na amwe yatumye serivisi za Kiliziya zitangwa binyuze kuri radiyo, imboneshakure cyangwa televiziyo, mu gihe andi arimo gutanga amasengesho yo gusengera mu modoka.
Mu gihe diyosezi ya Roma Gatolika yafunze insengero zayo n'insengero z'amasengesho, ndetse n'abahakorera ingendo z'ubukristo bava mu Kibuga cya Petero, izindi nzego z'amadini na zo zahagaritse imirimo mu nsengero, mu misigiti, mu nsengero z'Abayahudi, mu nsengero no mu bigo by'amasengero, kandi zigabanya amateraniro ya rusange.
Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Irani yatangaje ko amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu yahagaritswe mu turere twibasiwe n'icyorezo kandi nyuma yaho insengero zirafungwa, mu gihe Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abanyamahanga gusura insengero mu migi yera ya Mecca na Medina, ndetse n'abaturage.
Iki cyorezo cyateje ihungabana rikomeye cyane ku ngengabihe y'imikino ku isi kuva mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi.
Imikino myinshi ikomeye, harimo 201920 UEFA Champions League, 201920 Premier League, UEFA Euro 2020, 2019-20 NBA season, na 2019-20 NHL season, yahagaritswe cyangwa yasubitswe.
Icyorezo cyateje ibibazo gahunda ya Olimpiki y'impeshyi ya 2020, yari iteganyijwe gutangira mu mpera za Nyakanga; Komite Olempike Mpuzamahanga yatangaje ku ya 24 Werurwe ko iki gikorwa "kizasubikwa ku itariki itambutse 2020 ariko itarenze impeshyi ya 2021".
Ibi byatumye abakinnyi benshi bakina urusimbi bahindura uburyo bwo gukina kuri interineti, aho imbuga nyinshi z'imikino yo kuri interineti zavuze ko habayeho kwiyongera gukomeye kw'ibiciro by'ibimenyetso bishya. Uruganda rw'imyidagaduro na rwo rwagize ingaruka, hamwe n'amatsinda atandukanye y'umuziki yahagaritse cyangwa yahagaritse ibitaramo.
Amakinamico menshi akomeye nka Broadway na yo yahagaritse ibitaramo byose.
Bamwe mu bahanzi bashakishije uburyo bwo gukomeza no gusangira imirimo kuri enterineti, nko gukora imurikagurisha rya concert cyangwa "ibitaramo" bishingiye kuri web kugirango bamenyekanishe, batange kandi bamenyekanishe ibikorwa byabo.
Kuri interineti, ibintu byinshi byo kuri interineti bifite insanganyamatsiko ya coronavirus byakwirakwijwe nk'urwenya no guhangayika mu gihe nta cyizere gihari.
Kuva COVID-19 yaduka, abantu bafite inkomoko mu Bushinwa no mu Burasirazuba bwa Aziya, hamwe n'abantu bafite aho bakunze kuba mu Burayi, Amerika n'ahandi, bagiye bagaragazwaho urwikekwe, xenophobia n'ivangura.
Hari ibihugu byinshi, cyane cyane mu Burayi, Aziya y'iburasirazuba, Amerika ya Ruguru n'akarere ka Aziya-Pasifika, byabonye ibintu by'ubwoba, gushidikanya n'ubushyamirane.
