Nyuma y'uko icyorezo kigenda kizamuka mu bihugu bishya by'ibanze, abantu bo mu Butaliyani, igihugu cya mbere mu Burayi cyahuye n'icyorezo gikomeye cya COVID-19, na bo bashobora guhura n'ikibazo cyo gushidikanya no kwiheba. Abaturage bo mu bihugu birimo Malaysia, New Zealand, Singapore na Koreya y'Epfo, mu mizo ya mbere bashyize umukono ku busabe bwo kubuza Abashinwa kwinjira mu bihugu byabo mu rwego rwo kurwanya iki cyorezo.
