Abashinwa ndetse n'abandi Banya-Aziya bo mu Bwongereza na Amerika batangaje ko habayeho kwiyongera kw'ihohoterwa rishingiye ku moko, ndetse n'ibitero.
Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Donald Trump, yanenzwe cyane kubera ko yise coronavirus "Virus y'Abashinwa", ibyo byiswe n'abamunenga ko ari amacakubiri ashingiye ku moko kandi arwanya Abashinwa.
Abari mu myigaragambyo muri Ukraine bagabye igitero ku bisi zitwara abantu bavuye muri Ukraine n'abanyamahanga, ziva i Wuhan zijya i Novi Sarangari.
Abanyeshuri baturutse mu burasirazuba bw'amajyaruguru y'u Buhinde, buhana imbibi n'u Bushinwa, biga mu mijyi ikomeye y'u Buhinde, bivugwa ko bahuye n'ibitotezo bijyanye n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umuyobozi w'ishyaka rya Bharatiya Janata Party mu ntara ya West Bengal, Dilip Ghosh, yavuze ko Abashinwa barimbuye ibidukikije kandi "ni yo mpamvu Imana yabahaye guhora".
Nyuma yaho, ibiro by'ububanyi n'amahanga by'Abashinwa i Kolkata byamaganiye kure icyo gitekerezo, bivuga ko ari "ikosa". Mu Bushinwa, icyorezo cyateje imbere xenophobia n'ivangura ku baturage batari Abashinwa, byasobanuraga ko abanyamahanga ari "imyanda y'abanyamahanga" kandi ko ari abo "gushyira mu kato".
