Ubwongereza nabwo bwari bwaratangiye gukora ibikoresho byo gupima kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cya Koreya y'Epfo CognBiotech cyatangiye gukora icyiciro cyo gupima, PCR-based SARS-CoV-2 Test Kit (Powercheck Coronavirus) ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Igerageza gusobanura ubwoko bw'ingirabuzima fatizo "E" zisanganywe na koronavirusi zose za beta, cyane cyane RdRp, iboneka muri SARS-CoV-2. Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni kimwe mu bigo bya mbere byabonye icyifuzo cyo gukoresha byihuse ibikoresho byo gupima SARS-CoV-2 bishingiye kuri PCR biturutse ku Bushinwa National Medical Products Administration. Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) kirimo gutanga ikigo cyacyo cya 2019-novel coronavirus (2019-nCoV) RT-PCR mu gihe cy'umwanya nyawo ku bigo by'ubuvuzi rusange binyuze mu ikoranabuhanga mpuzamahanga.
Impinduka za kera z'ibikoresho by'isuzuma zagize ingaruka zitari zifatika kubera ko kimwe mu bipimo bitatu by'ibinyabuzima cyari gifite amakosa, kandi byateje ibibazo mu isuzuma rya CDC i Atlanta; byatumye ingero z'ibipimo byakozwe neza muri Gashyantare 2020 zose zigera munsi y'ingero 100 ku munsi.
Ibizamini bikoresha ibice bibiri ntibyemewe kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 kandi kugeza icyo gihe, ibigo bya leta n'ibikoresho by'ibanze ntibyemerewe gutangira ibizamini.
Ibizamini byemejwe na FDA mu buryo bw'ibanze. Ibitaro by'ubucuruzi byo muri Amerika byatangiye gukora ibizamini mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko COVID-19 igeragezwa rishingiye kuri RT-PCR iri kuboneka mu gihugu hose.
Quest Diagnostics yashyizeho uburyo bwo gupima COVID-19 mu gihugu hose kugeza ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta mipaka y'umubare yatangajwe; ingero zigomba gukusanywa no gutunganywa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, ikizamini cya COVID-19 cyakozwe kandi gitangwa n'ikigo cya Leta cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubwandu bw'indwara n'ikoranabuhanga VECTOR.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, iki kizamini cyanditswe na Federal Service for Surveillance in Healthcare. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, Mayo Clinic yamenyeshejwe ko irimo gukora ikizamini cyo gutahura ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Rush Diagnostics yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukora ikizamini mu byiciro bihanitse mu masaha 3.5, bituma kigira ibizamini bigera ku 4,128 bishobora gukorwa n'imashini imwe mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yahaye Abbott Laboratories uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa (EUA) rwo gukora ibizamini kuri m2000 ya Abbott; FDA yari yaratanze uruhushya nk'urwo mbere kuri Hologic, LabCorp, na ThermoFisher Scientific.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Sheffield na yo yabonye EUA ya FDA kugira ngo isuzume, ifata iminota igera kuri 45.
FDA yemeje ikigo cy'ubuvuzi gikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kongerera ingano ya nucleic acid (ACA) mu mwanya wa PCR.
Kubera ko bidasaba uruhererekane rw'ingendo z'ubushyuhe buhindagurika, ubu buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo byiza mu minota itageze kuri itanu n'ibisubizo bibi mu minota 13.
Ubu muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hari imashini zigera ku 18,000 nk'izo, kandi Abbott yifuza kongera ingano y'ibipimo ku munsi ku bipimo 50,000. Muri Tayiwani, ikigo cy'iperereza kirimo gukorwa gikoresha umuti wa monoclonal wihuza by'umwihariko na poroteyine ya nucleocapsid (N protein) ya coronavirus, mu byiringiro ko iyi poroteyine yihuta cyane ishobora gutanga ibisubizo mu minota 15 kugeza kuri 20 nk'uko bimeze ku bipimo bya virusi y'ibicurane.
