Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika cy'Ubuvuzi bw'Imirase cyatangaje ko CT itagomba gukoreshwa nk'ikigo cyo gupima cyangwa icyiciro cya mbere cyo gupima COVID-19. Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, CDC yemeza PCR nk'ikigo cy'ibanze cyo gupima.
