Zishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima ubwandu mu bantu guhera ku munsi wa 7 cyangwa nyuma yo gutangira kugaragaza ibimenyetso, no kugenzura abantu. Ibizamini bishobora gukorerwa muri Laboratwari z'ibanze (CLT) cyangwa hakoreshejwe ibizamini byo mu rwego rwo kugenzura (PoCT).
Ibizamini bizakorwa n'ibigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi bifite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini byinshi ariko kuboneka kwabyo bizaterwa n'ibipimo by'umusaruro wa buri kigo.
Ubusanzwe, ibipimo by'amaraso y'uruhande rumwe ni byo bikoreshwa muri CLT, ariko hashobora gukoreshwa ibindi bipimo byinshi kugira ngo harebwe uko abanduye bitabira indwara.
Urugero rumwe rw'amaraso yo gukoresha mu gupima indwara y'uruhu (PoCT) rukunze gutorwa mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga.
Intambwe ya mbere yo gukuraho ibizamini bitandukanye n'uburyo bwa PCR ntabwo isabwa. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, FDA yashyizeho ibigo 29 byatangaga amakuru kuri sosiyete iyo byabaga bikenewe, bityo ubu bikaba bishobora gutanga ibizamini by'ubudahangarwa.
Kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, hari ikizamini kimwe cyonyine cyaremewe na FDA munsi y'ububasha bwo gukoresha byihutirwa. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, EuroImmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics & Epitop Diagnostics yahawe uburenganzira bw'Uburayi ku bikoresho byayo by'ibizamini bishobora gutahura IgG na IgA byanduye virusi mu bipimo by'amaraso.
Ifite ubushobozi bwo gupima ibipimo amagana mu masaha make, bityo ikaba yihuta cyane kuruta ibipimo bisanzwe bya PCR bya RNA ya virusi.
Ubusanzwe abanduye bashobora kuboneka nyuma y'iminsi 14 icyorezo gitangiye. Mu ntangiriro za Mata, Ubwongereza bwabonye ko nta gikoresho na kimwe cyo gupima abanduye cy'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri baguze cyari cyiza ku buryo cyakoreshwa.
