Iyo umuganga ategetse ko habaho isuzuma, amafaranga y'isuzuma aba ari ayo kwishyurwa n'ubwishingizi.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na Robert Koch, umuyobozi w'ikigo, Ubudage bufite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini 160.000 mu cyumweru.
Gucunga imodoka mu mijyi minini byatangijwe kugeza ku ya 19 Werurwe.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, umubare w'ibizamini byose byakozwe mu Budage ntiwari uzi, kuko ibisubizo byiza gusa ari byo byatangajwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bw'urwego rw'iperereza bwagaragaje ko kugeza mu cyumweru cya 12/2020, nibura ibipimo 483,295 byasuzumwe, harimo n'icyumweru cya 12/2020, kandi ibipimo 33,491 (6.9%) byasuzumwe neza kuri SARS-CoV-2. Muri Israel, abashakashatsi bo mu bitaro bya Technion & Rembrandt bakoze uburyo bwo guhuriza hamwe ibipimo no kongera gusuzuma ibipimo by'abarwayi 64 icyarimwe, iyo ibipimo byasanganwe ko ari byiza. Mu buryo bwihutirwa, ikigo cya BGI cyashyizeho ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cya metero kare 2000 cyitwa "Huo-Yan" (mu gishinwa: 火眼, cyangwa "Fire Eye" mu cyongereza) cyatangijwe ku ya 5 Gashyantare 2020 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, gishobora gutunganya ibipimo birenga 10,000 ku munsi.
Hamwe no kugenzura imirimo y'ubwubatsi na Wang Jian washinze BGI, kandi bigatwara iminsi 5, icyitegererezo cyerekanye ko iyo ubushobozi bwo gupima butatangira, umubare w'ibyago muri Hubei wari kuba wiyongereyeho 47% kandi ibiciro bijyanye no guhangana na karantine byari bikubye kabiri.
