Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu - cyane cyane abantu bafite imimerere igoranye, nk'ababyeyi babyaye cyangwa abasirikare bakomerekeye mu bitaro - byamenyekanye bwa mbere mu kinyejana cya 19 rwagati n'abahanga babiri mu isuku y'intoki: umuganga w'Umunya-Hungariya Ignaz Semmelweis wakoreraga i Vienne, muri Autriche na Florence Nightingale, Umwongereza "washyizeho ubuvuzi bugezweho".
Icyo gihe abantu benshi batekerezaga ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi y'umubavu witwa miasma.
Mu myaka ya 1980, ibyorezo by'ibiribwa n'indwara ziterwa n'ubuzima byatumye Ikigo cya Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gihangayikishwa no kongera isuku y'intoki nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cya Virusi y'ibicurane mu 2009 na COVID-19 mu 2020 byateje ubukangurambaga mu bihugu byinshi ku kamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu kwirinda indwara zandura nk'izi.
Urugero, ibyapa byanditseho ngo "Ubuhanga bukwiriye bwo gukaraba intoki" byamanitswe hafi y'aho abantu bakarabira intoki mu bwiherero rusange no mu mazu y'ibiro no mu bwiherero bw'ibibuga by'indege mu Budage.
Amagambo ngo "gukaraba intoki" mu by'ukuri asobanura ko umuntu adashaka kugira uruhare mu kintu runaka.
Ryaturutse mu gice cya Matayo muri Bibiliya aho Ponsiyo Pilato yiyambuye icyemezo cyo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko cyaje kuba imvugo ikoreshwa cyane mu baturage bamwe na bamwe b'Icyongereza.
Muri Macbeth ya Shakespeare, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki ze mu buryo bwo guhatirwa mu kugerageza gukuraho ikizinga cyo mu mutwe, kigaragaza umutima we wicira urubanza ku byaha yakoze no kuba yarashishikarije umugabo we gukora ibyaha.
Basanze kandi ko abantu bakunze gukaraba intoki kenshi kurusha abandi, nyuma yo kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza ku bikorwa by'ubwiyandarike, kandi ko baha agaciro kenshi ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gutekereza batyo, ntibakunze gukora imirimo y'ubundi buryo bwo "gusukura" nk'ubw'ubwitange.
Amadini ategeka ko abantu bakaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku no mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo n'amazi adafite isabune yo gukaraba intoki ni kimwe mu bigize umuhango wo gukaraba intoki uvugwa mu madini menshi, harimo Aba-Bahá, Abahindu, Tewila na Netilat Yadayim mu idini rya Kiyahudi, Lavabo mu Bukristo, na Wazu mu idini rya Isilamu. Amadini na yo ategeka ko abantu bakaraba intoki mu buryo bwihariye kugira ngo batange isuku nyuma y'imirimo runaka.
Gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero ni itegeko mu idini rya Hindu, idini rya Kiyahudi n'idini rya Isilamu.
Kandi, gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kurya buri gihe ni itegeko mu idini rya Hindu, Buddhism, Sikhism, Yudaism na Islam.
Gutegeka ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 mu kazi
Kugenzura ibyago byo gukwirakwiza ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu kazi, ni imikoreshereze y'ibikorwa by'umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi, kugenzura ibyago, mu kwirinda indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Gutegeka neza ibyago byo gukwirakwira kw'indwara mu kazi biterwa n'aho umuntu akorera n'ibikorwa akora, bishingiye ku gusuzuma ibyago by'ahantu abantu bahuriye, uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibyago by'abakozi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA), imirimo y'ibyago byo guhura n'abantu bake ni yo ihura n'abantu bake n'abandi bakozi, aho inama z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zigirwa harimo: gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukurikiza imyitwarire yo guhumeka, no guhora basukura no guhumeka ahantu bakorera.
Imirimo y'ibyago byo guhura n'ibipimo byo hejuru ni iyo isaba guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegerana n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho ubwandu bwa COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye kubera ubwandu bw'umuryango cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri abo harimo abakozi bagirana imishyikirano n'abaturage muri rusange, urugero nk'amashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo abantu benshi, hamwe n'ibigo bimwe na bimwe bicuruza ibintu byinshi.
Uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago kuri iri tsinda zirimo: guhanahana umwuka n'imisogoto ikora neza, gukoresha indangururamajwi, no gukomeza ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite mu gihe umuntu wanduye COVID-19 ahura n'ikibazo.
OSHA ifata abakozi b'ubuzima n'abakora mu bigo by'ubuvuzi nk'abafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'umuntu urwaye cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19, kandi ibyo bishobora kwiyongera bigatuma bahura n'ibyago byinshi mu gihe abakozi bakoresha, bakorakoranya cyangwa bakorakora ibipimo ku muntu urwaye cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19 cyangwa bakoresha uburyo bwo gukora ibirungo by'umwuka.
Ibigo by'ubugenzuzi bw'ibyago bikwiye aba bakozi birimo inzego z'ubwubatsi nk'icyumba cy'itumanaho cy'umuvuduko utagira ingufu n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite bikwiye akazi.
Iterwa na COVID-19 rishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi mu kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutaza ku kazi kubera uburwayi, gukenera kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya guhura n'abandi.
Imiterere y'ubucuruzi ishobora guhinduka bitewe n'ibyo bicuruzwa bisabwa, n'uburyo bwo kubibona (urugero nk'igihe cyo kugabanuka kw'ibikenewe cyangwa kugura ibicuruzwa binyuze mu gutanga cyangwa mu bikorwa byo kugenda).
Amaherezo, urujya n'uruza rw'ibintu biturutse mu turere tuzwiho kuba twatewe na COVID-19 rushobora kugira ingaruka. Gutegura no gusubiza indwara yanduza bishobora gukoreshwa mu kuyobora ibikorwa by'ubwirinzi.
Imigambi ikemura ibipimo by'ibyago bitandukanye bifitanye isano n'ahantu h'akazi n'ibikorwa by'akazi, harimo isoko y'ibyago, ibyago bituruka mu rugo no mu baturage, hamwe n'ibyago by'abakozi ku giti cyabo nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Banasobanura ingamba z'ibanze zo guhangana n'ibiza, n'ingamba zo guhangana n'ibiza bishobora kuvuka mu gihe habaye icyorezo.
Gutegura no gusubiza ku ndwara zandura bishobora gukurikiza amabwiriza y'igihugu cyangwa y'akarere.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo zirimo: kugabanya ubwandu hagati y'abakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zidakwiriye, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bigo byo mu muyoboro wabo w'itangwa ry'ibiribwa.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho ubucuruzi bukorerwa bugira ingaruka ku bisubizo.
Gahunda y'ibigo by'ubugenzuzi bw'ibiza ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane mu gushyira hamwe ibigo by'ubugenzuzi bw'ibiza hakurikijwe ingaruka zabyo mu buvuzi n'umutekano mu kazi.
Aho ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora gukurwaho, inzego z'ibanze z'ibanze z'ibanze z'ibanze ni inzego z'ubwubatsi, zikurikirwa n'iz'ubuyobozi, hanyuma amaherezo ni ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Ingufu z'ubwubatsi zirimo gutandukanya abakozi n'ibibi bijyanye n'akazi, bitagendeye ku myitwarire y'umukozi, kandi bishobora kuba umuti uhenze cyane wo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Gutegeka ni impinduka mu mabwiriza cyangwa mu mikorere y'akazi bisaba igikorwa cy'umukozi cyangwa umukoresha.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwa bwite (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidakora neza cyane kuruta ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ibikoresho by'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda guhura n'abantu bamwe na bamwe.
Abakozi bagomba guhitamo ubwoko bwose bwa PPE hashingiwe ku kaga, kwambara ubwoko bukwiye (urugero, imashini zuhumeka), kwambara kenshi kandi neza, kugenzura buri gihe, kubungabunga no guhindura nkuko bikenewe, no gukuraho neza, gusukura no kubika cyangwa gutakaza kugirango birinde kwanduza.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA), akazi gafite ibyago byo guhura n'abantu bake gafite guhura n'abantu bake cyane n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zisabwa ahantu hose ho gukorera zirimo: gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, guha imyitwarire yo guhumeka ikingira ikorora no gusuhiramo, ibikoresho by'imyanda n'imyanda, gutegura amasaha yo guhindukira cyangwa amashanti igihe bibaye ngombwa, guca intege abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no guhora basukura no guhumanya ibidukikije by'akazi.
Kumenya no gushyira mu kato abantu bashobora kwandura mu gihe cya vuba mu kazi ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi.
Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) kirasaba ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze baguma mu rugo kugeza igihe badafite umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro, cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso mu gihe cy'amasaha 24 nta miti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti itera ibimenyetso, kandi ko gahunda z'ikiruhuko cyo kurwara zigira ubushobozi bwo kwemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bita kuri uwo muntu urwaye, kandi ko abakozi bamenya izo gahunda.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, imirimo y'ibyago byo guhura n'ibipimo byo hejuru ikubiyemo imirimo isaba guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegera abantu bari muri metero esheshatu (1.8m) batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'ubwandu bw'abaturage bukomeje gukwirakwira hafi y'aho bakorera, cyangwa bitewe n'uko uwo muntu aherutse gukora ingendo mpuzamahanga mu gace karimo ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
