Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzymes ifitanye isano n'ibice byo hanze by'ingirabuzimafatizo (urwihingiro rw'ingirabuzimafatizo) mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 igabanya imikorere ya angiotensin-transforming enzyme (ACE) ihuje na yo igabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II kandi igatuma angiotensin (1-7) yiyongera, bigatuma iba umuti wizewe wo kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora kandi nk'ahantu ho kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe.
Ubwoko bwa enzyme mu bantu akenshi buvugwa nka hACE2.
Angiotensin-transforming enzyme 2 ni metaloenzyme ifite zinc iri ku gice cy'imbere no ku bindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 igizwe n'udusobe tw'ibinyamubiri bya N-terminal peptidase M2 na C - terminal colectrine.
ACE2 ni ubwoko bwa I bwa poroteyine ya membrane ifite uruhande rumwe rwambuka hamwe na domaine ikora enzymatic ku mibiri y'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha no mu zindi nsoro.
Uruhare rwa ACE2 mu mubiri n'urundi rufite izina rya shades, ruca mu gice cy'urusobe, maze poroteyine ihinduka ikira mu maraso, igashyirwamo mu maraso.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifatanye cyane cyane n'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibice by'ubuhumekero by'ubwoko bwa II, intanga z'igifu, intanga z'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyoboro w'umuyo.
ACE2 mRNA igaragara mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa prostate, mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa striatum, mu gice cyitwa hypothalamus no mu gice cyitwa spine.
Imikorere y'ibanze ya ACE2 ni ugukora nk'igihombo cya ACE.
ACE igabanya ingirabuzima fatizo yitwa angiotensin I ikayigira angiotensin II.
ACE2 ihita yica amino acide phenylalanine ifite karboxyle mu gice cy'inyuma cya angiotensin II (Asp - Arg - Val - Tyr - Ile - His - Pro - Phe) ikayisenya mu mazi ikayigira angiotensin ikomeza imikorere (1 - 7), (H - Asp - Arg - Val - Tyr - Ile - His - Pro - OH).
ACE2 [des-Arg9] ishobora no gusenya izindi peptides nyinshi zirimo bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphin A na ghrelin.
ACE2 itegeka kandi gutwara mu gice cy'urwungano rwa amino acide itwara SLC6A19 kandi uruhare rwayo rwaravuzwe mu ndwara ya Heartburn.
Nk'indwara ya parenzyme, ACE2, ikora nk'ahantu hanini ho kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe zirimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 bihuza poroteyine S1 ku mibiri ku mibiri ku mibiri hamwe na ACE2 ku mibiri ku mibiri, bigatuma habaho endocytosis no kwimura virusi na enzymes mu mibiri mu mibiri.
Ubu buryo bwo kwinjira bukenera kandi ko poroteyine S itera inkunga n'umusemburo wa serine protease TMPRSS2, ubu ubufasha bwo kubuza biri mu byo iperereza riri gukoraho ubu buryo bwo kuvura. Ibyo byatumye bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya urugero rwa ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo bishobora gufasha kurwanya ubwandu.
Ariko kandi, inzego nyinshi z'umwuga n'izigenga zasabye ko hakomeza gukoresha imiti isanzwe ya ACE inhibitor na ARB.
Isesengura ryagaragaye ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012 ryakozwe mu buryo bufite gahunda n'isesengura ry'ibanze ryagaragaje ko "ikoreshwa rya ACE inhibitors rifitanye isano n'igabanuka ry'ibyago bya Pneumonia ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'ibikoresho byo kugenzura".
Byongeye kandi, "abarwayi bavurwa ACE inhibitors na bo bari bafite ibyago byo kurwara umusonga byagabanutse, bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara umusonga, cyane cyane mu bantu barwaye ikibazo cy'imvune n'umutima".
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors byanafitanye isano no kugabanya impfu ziterwa na nimoniya, nubwo ibisubizo byari bike cyane ugereranyije n'ibyago byose bya nimoniya".
Umuntu wongeye guhuza ACE2 (rhACE2) ifatwa nk'umuti mushya w'uburwayi bukabije bw'ibihaha, kandi byasaga n'aho byateza imbere haemodynamics y'ibihaha n'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu bana b'ingurube bafite indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze iterwa na lipopolysaccharide.
Mu bantu, igice cy'ubuzima bwa rhACE2 ni amasaha agera kuri 10 n'iminota 30 yo gutangira igikorwa, hamwe n'igihe cy'imirimo cy'amasaha 24.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bugaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti wizewe ku bantu bafite kutabogama ku buryo bwiza bwa Renin-Angiotensin System Inhibitors (RAS Inhibitors) cyangwa indwara zitera kuzamuka kwa angiotensin II. RhACE2 yasembuwe yagenzuwe mu bizamini byo kuvura indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye inkeke.
Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za software zigendanwa zashyizweho mu rwego rwo gufasha mu gukurikirana abantu, ni ukuvuga inzira yo kumenya abantu ("abahuye") bashobora kuba baragiranye isano n'umuntu wanduye, mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20.
Hariho porogaramu nyinshi zashyizweho cyangwa zatanzwe hamwe n'ubufasha bwa leta mu turere tumwe na tumwe n'ubutegetsi.
Hari imiterere myinshi y'uburyo bwo kubaka porogaramu zo gushakisha abakundana.
Hari impungenge ku byerekeye ubuzima bwite, cyane cyane ku buryo bwo gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Mu buryo bworoshye bwo guhagarika, harimo gukoresha ikimenyetso cya Bluetooth kugirango umenye aho umukozi aherereye n'indi telefoni igendanwa.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ku mugaragaro ko bagiye gushyira hamwe imikorere yo gushyigikira izo porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu zabo zikora za Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa yashyizeho porogaramu ikorana na Alipay, ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba barigeze guhura n'abantu barwaye COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore, porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether ikoreshwa.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango w'ikoranabuhanga wo muri ako gace, yasohotse nk'isoko ryuguruye kandi izashyikirizwa guverinoma. Macedonia ya Ruguru yatangije porogaramu ishingiye kuri Bluetooth "StopKorona!" kugirango imenye abo bantu bashobora kuba baranduye kandi itanga ibisubizo byihuse ku bayobozi b'ubuzima.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, guverinoma yavuze ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu yari mu cyiciro cyateye imbere cy'iterambere, kandi ko izaba iboneka mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyo ("StopCovid") nayo ikoreshwa muri Irilande no mu Bufaransa.
Australia na New Zealand byombi birimo gusuzuma porogaramu ya TraceTogether yo muri Singapore na porogaramu zishingiye kuri BlueTrace. Uburusiya bushaka gushyiraho porogaramu ya Geofencing ku barwayi basanzwemo COVID-19 baba i Moscou, igamije kubemeza ko batagomba kuva mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yagaragaje ibibazo byinshi bishobora kuvuka mu mikorere ishingiye kuri porogaramu, harimo ibibazo by'ibinyoma n'ubushobozi buke bushobora kubaho niba ikoreshwa rya porogaramu rihagarariye igice gito cy'abaturage.
Mu guhangana n'impungenge ku ikwirakwira rya porogaramu za "coronavirus" z'uburiganya cyangwa zangiza, Apple yagennye ubwoko bw'imiryango ishobora gushyira porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus muri App Store yayo, ikabigabanya ku miryango "yemewe" gusa cyangwa irebwa.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho ibihano nk'ibyo.
Abashinzwe umutekano mu by'ibanga bagaragaje impungenge bafite ku bijyanye n'ingaruka z'ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi mu buryo bunini hakoreshejwe porogaramu za coronavirus, cyane cyane niba ibikorwa remezo by'ubushakashatsi byakozwe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus bizasenyuka nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo kirangiye.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 yasohoye itangazo rigamije gushyira imipaka ku bikorwa nk'ibi byo kugenzura.
Amashyirahamwe yatangaje ibintu umunani ku mishinga ya leta:
Igenzura rigomba kuba "ryemewe, rikenewe kandi rifite igipimo";
hagomba kuba igice cy'iherezo cyo kugenzura no kugenzura ibisobanuro;
Gukoresha amakuru bigomba kuba mu rwego rwo kwirinda COVID-19;
Umutekano n'ubwisungane mu gutanga amakuru bigomba kurindwa kandi bigaragazwa ko byarinzwe bishingiye ku bimenyetso;
Igenzura ry'ikoranabuhanga rigomba kwirinda guteza imbere ivangura no gutesha agaciro;
gusangira amakuru n'abantu batatu bigomba gusobanurwa n'amategeko;
hagomba kubaho uburyo bwo kurinda uburenganzira bw'abaturage mu guhangana n'ihohoterwa no kurirwanya;
"Kugira uruhare rwuzuye" bizakenerwa n'abantu bose "bafite aho babogamiye", harimo impuguke mu by'ubuzima rusange n'amatsinda adafite ububasha. Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga cyitwa The German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) na Reporters Without Borders (Reporters Without Borders) (RSF) na byo byasohoye urutonde.
Igitekerezo cya Google / Apple kigamije gukemura ikibazo cyo kugenzura buri gihe, gukuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana mubikoresho byabo bikora igihe bidakenewe.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byakoresheje igenzura ry'ahantu hashingiye ku muyoboro aho gukoresha porogaramu, bikuraho icyifuzo cyo gukuramo porogaramu hamwe n'ubushobozi bwo kwirinda gukurikirana.
Muri Isirayeli, gukurikirana hakoreshejwe umuyoboro byemewe.
Ibisubizo bishingiye ku muyoboro bifite amakuru y'ahantu atagenzuwe bifite ibibazo bikomeye byibanga byibanga.
Ariko, sisitemu zose zifite seriveri nkuru ntabwo zisaba kugera kumakuru yimyanya yihariye; sisitemu nyinshi zirinda ubuzima bwite zashyizweho zikoresha seriveri nkuru gusa kugirango zivugane (reba igice gikurikira).
Uburyo butari bushingiye kuri porogaramu bwakoreshejwe mu gukurikirana abantu muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, sisitemu yakusanyije amakuru yo gukurikirana aturutse ahantu hatandukanye harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga hamwe namakuru yo gutumanaho kw'ikarita, maze ayashyira hamwe kugirango atange imenyesha ku bantu bashobora kwandura binyuze mu butumwa bwanditse.
Usibye gukoresha aya makuru kugira ngo bamenyeshe abantu bashobora kuba bahuye, leta yashyizeho amakuru y'aho umuntu ari kubera impinduka zikomeye mu mategeko y'ibanga ry'amakuru nyuma y'icyorezo cya MERS muri icyo gihugu.
Aya makuru aboneka ku baturage binyuze muri porogaramu nyinshi na website. Ibihugu byinshi birimo n'Ubudage byatekereje gukoresha uburyo bwo gushyiraho inzego zishinzwe umutekano no kurinda ubuzima bwite.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, ibyo bisobanuro ntibyari byaratanzwe.
Kurinda ubuzima bwite ni igitekerezo cyashyizweho neza, hamwe n'ibitabo byinshi by'ubushakashatsi guhera nibura mu 2013. Kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'inzobere arenga icumi yakoraga ku bisubizo byujuje ubuziranenge, nk'ikoreshwa rya Bluetooth low energy (BLE) kugirango umenye aho umukozi aherereye n'izindi telefoni zigendanwa.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni umuhate wo guhuza uburyo bwiganjemo ubwiganze n'ubwiganze, kandi ntabwo ari protocole imwe. Porotokolo ziganjemo izo gucunga ubuzima bwite (DP-PPT/DP-3T), nimero z'imishyikirano z'igihe gito (TCN, yahoze ari contact event number, CEN), protocol iharanira ubuzima bwite n'uburyo bwo gukurikirana imishyikirano ya telefoni ngendanwa (PACT) n'ibindi.
Muri izi protocole, amakuru y'umuntu ku giti cye atajya hanze y'igikoresho, kandi imikoranire yose iba ku gikoresho.
Itsinda ry'ibanga muri MIT Media Lab ririmo gukora SafePaths, urubuga rwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kurinda ubuzima bwite mu gukusanya no gukoresha amakuru ajyanye n'aho umuntu ari cyangwa inzira anyuramo mu gukurikirana ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe na Whitepaper "Aps Gone Rogue: Kubungabunga ubuzima bwite muri iki cyorezo" yasohowe muri Werurwe 2020. Igikorwa nk'iki ni SafeTrace ikorwa n'ikigo gishinzwe guteza imbere ikoranabuhanga ry'ibanga Enigma MPC, cyashinzwe mbere muri MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga ry'ibikoresho bifite umutekano, bituma abakoresha bashobora gusangira amakuru y'ahantu no ku buzima n'abandi bakoresha n'abayobozi batarenganyije ku bwisanzure bw'ayo makuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, Inteko mpuzamahanga y'ubufatanye ya TCN yashinzwe n'amatsinda yateguwe mu buryo bw'ingengabitekerezo imwe kandi hakurikijwe amabwiriza amwe agamije kugabanya amacakubiri, no guhuza porogaramu zo gushakisha no kuburira, ari nabyo byari ingenzi mu kugera ku buryo bukomeye.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, Guverinoma ya Singapuru yatangaje ko yashyize hanze protocole ya BlueTrace ikoreshwa na porogaramu yayo ya leta.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo bigenzura imbuga za Android na iOS, byatangaje gahunda yo gukurikirana abakorana, bavuga ko izaba ifite ubushobozi bwo kurinda ubuzima bwite bushingiye ku ikoranabuhanga ryoroshye rya Bluetooth hamwe na cryptography irinda ubuzima bwite.
Yasohoye kandi ibisobanuro byikoranabuhanga ryingenzi rikoreshwa muri sisitemu.
Nk'uko Apple na Google babivuga, iyi gahunda igomba gutangwa mu byiciro bitatu:
Gutanga ibikoresho bifasha guverinoma gukora porogaramu zishinzwe kurinda ubuzima bwite bwa leta-koronavirusi.
Iyi mikorere ikora neza cyane kuri iOS na Android
Gusubiza mu buryo imiti (nanone izwi nko kongera gukoresha imiti, kongera kubara, kongera gushyiraho cyangwa guhindura uburyo bwo kuvura), ni ugusubiza mu buryo imiti yemewe kuvura indwara cyangwa ubuzima butandukanye n'ubwo yatangijwe mbere.
Ni uburyo bw'ubushakashatsi mu bya siyansi bukoreshwa muri iki gihe mu gukora imiti ya COVID-19 ifite umutekano kandi igira ingaruka nziza.
Mu bindi byerekeranye n'ubushakashatsi harimo iterambere ry'urukingo rwa COVID-19 no gutera amaraso mu mubiri. SARS-CoV-2 ifite poroteyine zigera kuri 66 zigamije, buri imwe ifite ahantu henshi hahuza ligand.
Gusuzuma ibyo bice by'ubufatanye bitanga umushinga ukwiriye wo gukora imiti ikingira virusi ikingira poroteyine za COVID-19.
Muri poroteyine z'ingenzi SARS-CoV-2 yibasira harimo protease ya Papane-like, RNA-dependent RNA polymerase, helicase, S protein na ADP ribophosphate.
Hussain n'abandi bize imiti myinshi y'abakandida, hanyuma bayihindura kandi bayisesengura kugira ngo ihure cyane n'imiti yemewe nk'iyo kugira ngo yihutishe iterambere ry'umuti w'ingaruka wa SARS-CoV-2 mu bushakashatsi bwa mbere yo kwipimisha bwasabwe mu buryo bw'ubushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi.
Chloroquine ni umuti urwanya malariya ukoreshwa kandi mu kurinda indwara zimwe na zimwe ziterwa n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
Ku ya 18 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine ifitanye isano na yo, izaba iri mu miti ine iri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi rya Solidarity.
Guverineri wa New York, Andrew Cuomo, yatangaje ko ibizamini bya leta ya New York kuri Chloroquine na Hydroxychloroquine bizatangira ku ya 24 Werurwe. Ku ya 28 Werurwe, FDA yemeje ikoreshwa rya Hydroxychloroquine Sulfate na Chloroquyl Phosphate mu buryo bw'Igenamigambi ry'Icyorezo (EUA).
Umuti ntabwo wemejwe na FDA mu buryo bw'igerageza ry'ibizamini byo kwa muganga kandi wemewe gusa muri EUA nk'umuti w'igerageza wo gukoresha byihutirwa mu barwayi bari mu bitaro ariko badashobora kuvurwa mu igerageza ryo kwa muganga.
CDC yavuze ko "imikoreshereze, dosiye cyangwa igihe hydroxychloroquine ikoreshwa mu gukumira cyangwa kuvura indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 itarashyirwaho".
Abaganga bavuze ko bakoresha imiti mu gihe "nta bundi buryo buhari".
Itsinda ry'ubushakashatsi ryo muri Turukiya riri i Istanbul ririmo gukora ubushakashatsi buto ku ikoreshwa rya Chloroquine hamwe na zinc, vitamini A, vitamini C na vitamini D.
Hari ubushakashatsi bukomeye buri gukorwa muri kaminuza ya Duke na Oxford.
Ishuri ry'ubuvuzi rya NYU Langone ririmo gukora igerageza ku mutekano n'ubushobozi bwo kwirinda hydroxychloroquine.
Ibizamini byo mu Bushinwa byabereye i Wuhan na Shenzhen byavuze ko favipiravir "ifite ubushobozi bugaragara".
Abarwayi 35 bo muri Shenzhen bagaragaje ko banduye mu gihe cy'iminsi 4, mu gihe abarwayi 45 batanduye bagaragaje ko banduye mu gihe cy'iminsi 11.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe ku barwayi 240 bafite indwara y'umwijima i Wuhan, kimwe cya kabiri cy'abarwayi bahawe favipiravir, ikindi kimwe cya kabiri bahabwa omyfenovir.
Ikigo cy'Ubuvuzi cy'Ubutaliyani cyibukije abaturage ko ibimenyetso biriho bishyigikira uyu muti ari bike kandi ko ari ibisanzwe.
